{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 3227699, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Boxofbeer", "body": "[b][npc=164547][/b] rare mob can be found in [b][zone=11510][/b].\n[ul]\n[li][b]Location[/b]: 50.34 20.99[/li]\n[li][b]Required for[/b]: [achievement=14309][/li]\n[li][b]Rare drop:[/b] [b][item=182179] [/b][/li]\n[/ul]\n[b][npc=164547][/b] runs around the spot and there is nothing hard in this fight.\nJust clear the area as rare charges back and there and may overpull wildlife around there.\nLoot [b][item=182179] [/b] and turn in the quest to unlock new skin for [b][spell=310143][/b]\n\n[quote]\n[u][b]TomTom coordinates:[/b][/u]\n\n/way 50.34 20.99 Mystic Rainbowhorn\n[/quote]\n[b][npc=164547][/b] rare mob location - https://youtu.be/1PgAbYaGRD8", "date": "2020-09-05T01:39:09-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-09-05T01:40:59-05:00", 1, "Boxofbeer"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 3233132, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "varenne", "body": "[npc=164547] is located in the [zone=11510] zone.\n\nTo summon this rare someone in the area need to use [object=345446]. \nIt will spawn Rainbowhorn with big hp pull.\nRare will start running around the area. you can see possible map attached to this page [npc=164547]\n\n\nFight is nothing special, but the rare can drop a reward quest item  [item=182179].\nThis quest item is relevant only for Night Fay Covenant players and will give you a Runestag [spell=310143] form after you turn in the [quest=62434]\n\n\nRare is a part of [achievement=14309] achievement.\n[quote][b]\nMystic Rainbowhorn Possible spawn locations:\n/way 49.72 19.72 \n/way 65.51 29.11 \nPossible Great horn of Runestage locations:\n/way 25.01 50.01\n/way 27.01 45.03 \n/way 39.02 60.01\n/way 30.04 36.10\n/way 41.31 71.21\n/way 44.80 19.18\n/way 50.01 20.03\n/way 55.41 55.81\n/way 58.37 61.04\n[/b][/quote]\nMystic Rainbowhorn video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eKg2WULGHd8", "date": "2020-09-26T05:17:31-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I was able to get this as Venthyr - but unable to hand in as you need to access the Wild Hunt Central area", "creationdate": "2020-11-25T03:08:49-06:00", "id": 1410050, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3233132, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "unbeaten3", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "no longer requires horn in live Shadowlands, that was only in Beta.", "creationdate": "2020-11-26T21:29:41-06:00", "id": 1411749, "rating": 4, "commentid": 3233132, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "LiriusMagi", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Horn has been hotfixed as of 11/27/2020. A horn was found on our realm and blown, rare was spawned afterwards. Did not spawn on it's own.", "creationdate": "2020-11-27T22:22:15-06:00", "id": 1412820, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3233132, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Koiyama", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "new coordinate for the runestag horn found at: 31.45, 46.17", "creationdate": "2020-12-03T15:02:02-06:00", "id": 1418579, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3233132, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "MrCrippels", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "found one at 33, 45, i didnt see it on the list", "creationdate": "2020-12-10T22:38:49-06:00", "id": 1424093, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3233132, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "maddiedalsing", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-12-01T15:53:14-06:00", 8, "varenne"]}
