{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 3256415, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "juress", "body": "I was killing the mobs in heartwood grove and out of nowhere I see in chat that I summoned this rare. Before I was able to find it near Tirna Vaal, it was already down to 1/3 of its health and what's best - it was tagged by horde... I was mad as hell.", "date": "2020-11-26T12:30:54-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 3256642, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "akarisuicide", "body": "I had the emote spam out in my name, and I had no idea what it meant so I consulted Wowhead. I looked for the Mystic Rainbowhorn rare, and it did indeed spawn... and it most definitely killed me. Easily. After finding my body, I looked for it again but it seemed to despawn.\r\n\r\nI hadn't used any item, and definitely didn't have a [object=345446] at all, so I think this is a bug.\r\n\r\n[b]tl;dr: Didn't have this item, didn't use this item, emote went out, rare was spawned, promptly killed me. Bug.[/b]\r\n\r\nEdit: Happened [i]again [/i]the very next day. Was fighting a mob, and the emote went out randomly. Didn't loot or blow the horn. I'm not going to submit a bug report though, because I figure a rare that is being spawned for [i]free[/i]? That's kinda nice.[i] :3[/i]", "date": "2020-11-26T15:07:06-06:00", "rating": 10, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Same. It might be random from killing mobs. Today I channeled my conductor to Dreamsong Fenn and after killing one rare, my chat said I had spawned it.", "creationdate": "2020-11-26T16:11:10-06:00", "id": 1411557, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3256642, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Caelus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Same sort of thing happened to me. I was on the spot to use horn. It wasnt there. I went AFK to get a drink. Got back, did a little herbing and the emote went out. Went to check where it spawns and nothing. No rare.", "creationdate": "2020-11-26T16:38:28-06:00", "id": 1411571, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3256642, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Unfknblvble", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I've yet to see this rare spawn, I spend the entire day in Ardenweald but nothing. did dailies, rares, killing random mobs. But nothing.. I wonder what the spawn timer is for this.", "creationdate": "2020-11-26T17:01:22-06:00", "id": 1411590, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3256642, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "meowzsa", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I had the emote popping up with my name while sorting bags and disenchanting stuff in Tirna Vaal at level 59 and no part of the night fae covenant ^^", "creationdate": "2020-11-27T04:09:36-06:00", "id": 1411999, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3256642, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "minakatze", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I was afk, & came back to see the emote had gone off 5min prior to my return. Went to glitterfalls, nothing. Everyone seems to be saying it spawns North of Tirna Vaal now, so going to camp there tonight. Edit: Got it when I camped him north of Tirna Vaal!", "creationdate": "2020-11-27T16:59:22-06:00", "id": 1412562, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3256642, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Wolfofthenyght", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 3256894, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Jamein", "body": "Emote went out saying I had summoned him when I hadn't clicked anything. Others in General were saying they also got the emote with their name in it.\n[s]Tag appears to be limited to 5 people. We had a raid attack it and only 5 got to loot out of the 22 in raid.[/s]\n\nTag issue is fixed, tested 1/12/2020. Everyone should now get loot from hitting this rare.", "date": "2020-11-26T18:20:52-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-12-01T16:01:55-06:00", 3, "Jamein"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 3256913, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "corvidia", "body": "Currently there appears to be a bug? in which this mob can be faction tagged/tagged by a limited number of people. Or at least I hope it's a bug; if it's intentional, I gotta say, that was a terrible idea on Blizz's part. Either way, if you're hoping to try for the runestag drop, be ready for a competition.", "date": "2020-11-26T18:46:37-06:00", "rating": 50, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I was fighting it with a small handful of other people, and its nameplate turned gray on me mid-fight. I didn't get the stag soul.", "creationdate": "2020-11-27T00:24:54-06:00", "id": 1411859, "rating": 10, "commentid": 3256913, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Koumaru", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Faction tag has always been a thing on rares", "creationdate": "2020-11-28T15:48:43-06:00", "id": 1413589, "rating": -30, "commentid": 3256913, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Unknowiii", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I really hope this is a bug, it was really disheartening that it turned grey as soon as I hit it, after spending an hour trying to spawn it and then tag it in time...", "creationdate": "2020-11-30T02:34:39-06:00", "id": 1415148, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3256913, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Fyana", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
