{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 3257603, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "plebl", "body": "Spawns at 65.5, 29.1 every 2-3 hours on live. Patrols south going towards Tirna Vaal. It doesn't live for very long if it gets near town, tag quick because only a few people can get loot.\n\nI camped at the north entrance of Tirna Vaal, no mobs that'll kill you while you're waiting.\n\nHorn emote will go out saying you've rung the horn telling you it's spawned. I never rung the horn while waiting for the spawn or have seen the horn spawn. Pretty bizarre beta and live spawn locations/requirements are so different.\n\nEdit: Looks like the emote is correct now and you need to click the horn to spawn (12/05/20).", "date": "2020-11-27T08:05:44-06:00", "rating": 17, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "YEP. Thank you SO, SO much! I just got it tonight! Seems that it's on a 2hr spawn timer with about a 10min randomizer. Got emote #1 at 5:44pm, missed that spawn (went to the old area) Got emote #2 at 8:34pm - spawned right on top of me at /way 65.5, 29.1 and got the soul!", "creationdate": "2020-11-27T19:46:17-06:00", "id": 1412710, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3257603, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Wolfofthenyght", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Can confirm this is true! I camped the spawn point for an hour and he spawned a few feet in front of me. Dropped the Runestag Soul for me", "creationdate": "2020-11-28T14:54:38-06:00", "id": 1413526, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3257603, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DireWolfKas", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Currently waiting at 3 hours and still nothing, will update as soon as I do see it. *Edit: Made it to 7 hours in total and it didn't spawn at this location. I'll try going over to the old horn location tomorrow to see if it's back to what it used to be.", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T00:22:59-06:00", "id": 1413964, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3257603, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Yaoqin", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I'm at 2.5 hours right now and no spawn, even after server reset. I have WM off.", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T11:36:56-06:00", "id": 1414436, "rating": -1, "commentid": 3257603, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "mshep02", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "This is not correct. You have to blow the horn. Read other comments for locations. I also posted a screenshot, waiting for it to approve.", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T12:25:08-06:00", "id": 1414488, "rating": 4, "commentid": 3257603, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Zixx7", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-12-05T21:05:04-06:00", 1, "plebl"]}
