{"commentv2": 1, "number": 16, "id": 3258463, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "SimiusMortis", "body": "Spawned at 65, 29 for me too (road above Tirna Vaal), only took 3 of us to down, had about 500k health. Don't have exact spawn time but I was waiting there for a couple of hours.\r\nSpawned after \"*insert username* has blown the Great Horn of the Runestag, luring the Mystic Rainbowhorn out into the open.\" \r\nI am level 60, Night Fae. 2/9 Night Fae Campaign but not sure if that matters.", "date": "2020-11-27T21:18:28-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
