{"commentv2": 1, "number": 19, "id": 3258650, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Ryodoan", "body": "This mob can reset if you pull into town. I'm on horde side. Alliance dragged him into town and reset. Then they got first hit and it was greyed out for me and I got no loot at the end. :( Not sure if bug or not since it is a rare, I thought it would be lootable for both factions. Not the case for me. Not sure if anyone else has seen that happen.", "date": "2020-11-28T01:51:34-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 3259820, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "drainbamaged", "body": "I call bs on this 2-3 hrs spawn timer. My group and I have waited well over 4 hrs at his spawn for nothing. Need more clarification if he spawns in a singular location or throughout the zone.", "date": "2020-11-28T22:07:13-06:00", "rating": -8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It wont spawn unless the horn is clicked. It is not random.", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T12:14:35-06:00", "id": 1414479, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3259820, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Zixx7", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 21, "id": 3260013, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Aurican", "body": "On live as of 11/29/20 you definitely need to blow the horn to spawn him. I have spent a lot of time in Ardenweald and thought it was crazy that I never saw the emote for him spawning if he was actually a timed spawn, so I went looking for the horn. I found the horn at 44.8, 19.18. My gf was sitting camping his spawn point north of Tirna Vaal at 65.74, 28.43 and as soon as I clicked the horn he spawned by her. He was rather hard hitting and was wrecking her hunter pet, but I could take a couple hits as a havoc DH while she revived her pet then heal back up with leech and we killed it duo.\r\n\r\nI didn't take a screenshot of the horn up because I didn't think about it at the time, if the horn is there some other time I'll grab a screenshot to submit.\r\n\r\nWe are both night fae and the soul shape quest item dropped for both of us.\r\n\r\nI made an account specifically for this post since there was no accurate information anywhere about it, so hope you all enjoy and good luck!\r\n\r\nTL:DR Horn at 44.8 19.18, rare at 54.74 28.43", "date": "2020-11-29T02:52:11-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just wondering what server were you on? :)", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T04:05:48-06:00", "id": 1414101, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3260013, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "inskst", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Tichondrius. I was the hunter :D", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T04:55:40-06:00", "id": 1414132, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3260013, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Charayvia", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The horn is very big. It was sitting on the ground to the left of the little setting with the two tables with the harps on them. It may have multiple spawn points. That was the first place Aurican and I had seen it.", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T05:52:41-06:00", "id": 1414174, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3260013, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Charayvia", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 22, "id": 3260095, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Marallie", "body": "Found Horn today at 27 45. If the Mystic Rainbowhorn is not spawning in your realm check the zones with ellites in it :)\nAnother location i found: 55 55,73", "date": "2020-11-29T04:32:22-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "just created an account. Can confirm this 100% just got it. Had 5 people in group one waiting at 65,5/29,1(Legit spawn location), one at 44,8/19.18, 48/xx. Waited for 2 hours and then i went checking on this location (27/45)after it just got posted. Horn was there surrounded by many mythics. 100% real info Rang the horn and the rare spawned instantly on 65.5/29.1", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T04:55:06-06:00", "id": 1414131, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3260095, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DDex7", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-11-29T04:58:30-06:00", 2, "Marallie"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 23, "id": 3260160, "nreplies": 26, "sticky": 0, "user": "Yaoqin", "body": "Just making a quick post consolidating what I've come to realize while camping this guy. It has been confirmed by a few comments here and comments on the [object=345446] page that the horn indeed spawns in different locations around the zone now. The horn is exactly how this mob spawns, and it's the horn, not the mob that is on the respawn timer. \n\n[i]Spawn Points For The Rare:[/i]\n[code]\n/way 65.5, 29.1\n[/code]\n\nYou can indeed wait in this spot and hope someone else hits a horn, but ideally you should have someone look for a horn while you camp. Setting your hearthstone to Tirna Vaal seems to be a good option as the rare seems to stick to the top area of the map. [b][i]This mob can be reset if pulled too far.[/i][/b]\n\nThe tag issue on this mob appears to have been fixed as well.\n\n[i]Horn Locations We Know So Far:[/i]\n[code]\n/way 27, 45\n/way 44.8,19.18\n/way 50, 20\n/way 58.37, 61.04\n/way 41, 71\n/way 55.4, 55.8\n/way 25, 50\n/way 39, 60\n/way 30,36\n[/code]\n\nIf you happen across a different horn location or another spawn location, please comment it below and I will periodically add them to my list as they are confirmed by multiple people.", "date": "2020-11-29T05:44:38-06:00", "rating": 120, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Found Horn at 41.24, 71.63 . handy trick is to set hearthstone at Tirna Vaal to meet the rare on the path.", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T18:14:09-06:00", "id": 1414822, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3260160, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Marshmallowy", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Found a horn earlier today, we clicked it and the emote played out but NOTHING spawned. We were at the exact spawn site described above, and when we didn't find it we looked at other \"spawn sites\", still nothing. Sigh.", "creationdate": "2020-11-30T20:09:45-06:00", "id": 1415978, "rating": 6, "commentid": 3260160, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Avandaline", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I found the horn at 30, 36 in The Stalks! Thank you for the info; had a friend wait at the spawn for so they could tag it since I was all the way across the zone. :)", "creationdate": "2020-12-01T04:42:00-06:00", "id": 1416304, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3260160, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Akiotena", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Horn just spawned at Darkreach point, around the 39,60 point. Was about 5 hrs of waiting. Mystic Rainbowhorn spawned on the north road of Tirna Vaal. Dont forget to set hearth to Tirna Vaal before you camp out the way points, so you can hearth back up and run up the north road to catch the spawn. GL!", "creationdate": "2020-12-02T20:40:18-06:00", "id": 1417921, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3260160, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "rbynplz", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "This really should be the top post. All confirmed. I found the horn tonight inside the hut at 58.37, 61.04, blew on it, and immediately hearthed back to Tirna Vaal, and then rode north. The rare had almost made it to town at that point. I followed it in stealth (feral druid) until more people caught up with it, and it had gone considerably west of Tirna Vaal by then. With only two of us, it killed us pretty quickly, but once we had 4 people the fight went smoothly. Received the runestag soulshape quest item once it was defeated.", "creationdate": "2020-12-06T19:17:17-06:00", "id": 1421378, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3260160, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "NecroBones", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2021-03-04T16:34:56-06:00", 14, "Yaoqin"]}
