{"commentv2": 1, "number": 30, "id": 3264344, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Bananasaur", "body": "Found [object=345446] at 67.79, 54.84\n\nI already have the Soulshape form so I announced it in General and gave people the time to get to 65.5, 29.1 where [npc=164547] spawns. \n\nOnce everyone was there and happy, he spawned at that location, everyone got a tag and everyone was able to loot. The lower level people mentioned they could not loot [item=182179]  so I am guessing it's for 60 only. \n\nHope this helps :)", "date": "2020-12-02T11:49:12-06:00", "rating": 14, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-12-07T19:28:01-06:00", 1, "Bananasaur"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 31, "id": 3265825, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "raibbe", "body": "Camped the known spawns with 6+ members. Took 2,5h+ for horn to spawn.\r\n\r\nIf you have killed the rare before choosing night fae as your covenant, you don't get the quest item on 2nd kill, but you still get the form and can change it from the NPC.", "date": "2020-12-03T19:28:57-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 32, "id": 3266696, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Crusalis", "body": "I found the horn around 38, 58 by one of the pieces of the Cache of the Moon. Thinking it would just give me a buff, I clicked it and the emote rang out across the zone. Jokes on me since it appears to spawn all the way on the opposite side from where I was.", "date": "2020-12-04T14:00:16-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
