{"commentv2": 1, "number": 34, "id": 3267597, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Bleachrush", "body": "Joined a raid to search for it, here what happened:\r\n\r\n1. Found the horn around 67,54\r\n2. The spawn was at around 65,29\r\n3. All raid was able to tag it\r\n4. All who were Night Fae did get the quest drop (so that confirms 100%?)\r\n5. People who were not Night Fae with us didn't get the drop", "date": "2020-12-05T13:11:46-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 35, "id": 3269962, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "frihedstimen", "body": "Thank you Blizzard! Just used the horn at 38.40 - 65.90 DarkspearEU wmoff grp. The emote was in chat. Mystic Rainbowhorn ..spawnd at 65.00 - 29.00, non of us got any tag, befor it was dead, killed by others!", "date": "2020-12-08T03:55:30-06:00", "rating": 21, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just happened to me too. Had to travel across Ardenweald to get there and managed to miss the tag by seconds before it died right in front of me.", "creationdate": "2021-01-03T21:27:36-06:00", "id": 1436033, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3269962, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "kooyking", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 36, "id": 3271469, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "angiedoll", "body": "I recommend doing this early morning for less competition.\r\n\r\nLogged in at 5am, found horn at the south middle location, rushed to his spawn point. There were already 2 people attacking and found him at half health.\r\n\r\nBut I got the soul shape! One of the best soul shapes if not the best", "date": "2020-12-10T08:09:01-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 37, "id": 3272377, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Caitness", "body": "I've seen a ton of people say the horn isn't necessary. I camped Mystic Rainbowhorn's spawn all day yesterday while occasionally going out to search for the horn. Neither the horn or the rare spawned at all yesterday (horn was likely in an, as yet, unlisted location). Decided to do a round for the horn before doing dailies today (11DEC). Found it just south of Hibernal Hollow near Wrigglemortis at /way 58, 61 in a building with a Fae and her cat. Rare spawned near /way 65, 28\r\n\r\nYou definitely need to try and do this with at least one other person. If that isn't possible, set your hearth to Tirna Vaal.", "date": "2020-12-11T12:46:51-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 38, "id": 3273112, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "KushoLion", "body": "Unsurprisingly, people don't actually share where the mob is when they blow the horn in-game, given it appears to not show up in the same spot. So if you, like me, see the announcement in-game that someone blew the horn, don't expect to actually get to tag the boss if you aren't already directly on top of wherever it decides to spawn, because you won't get there in time.", "date": "2020-12-12T14:51:07-06:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 39, "id": 3278328, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Argus00", "body": "Found the horn @ 44, 19, ran over to 49, 19 hoping to find him there. Obviously, Blizz trolled me and had him spawn @ 65, 29, so I mounted up and ran there (HS was set to Revendreth, fml...), even though I was already sure I'd missed him yet again. He wasn't there, I thought he'd been killed but didn't see a corpse. I headed to Tirna Vaal to take a flight path to do other stuff, and on my minimap I saw the silver arrow pointing to a shiny. I headed that way and caught the [npc=164547] @ 57, 35 - he was running (slower than a player mounted) on the path heading to Glitterfall Basin. Tagged, tanked, got the soulform.\n\nMy guess is if he spawns @ 65, 29 he runs to 49, 19 to, I don't know, camp there?", "date": "2020-12-21T13:13:46-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-12-21T13:20:01-06:00", 2, "Argus00"]}
