{"commentv2": 1, "number": 41, "id": 3287324, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "xNiaa", "body": "Can confirm that it takes [b]around 2 hours[/b] for the horn to respawn. \r\nWhen I found the horn for the first time (50, 20), I ported to Tirna Vaal instantly but couldn't find the rare anywhere. Also no one announced the location in the chat or created a group. \r\nFound the horn again at the same location after 110 minutes and this time also the rare at 65.5, 29.1 (north of TV).", "date": "2021-01-07T16:48:36-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
