{"commentv2": 1, "number": 43, "id": 3299973, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "JulesPaece", "body": "To sum up all knowledge about horn spawn points until Feb 17th here you are with 2 macros (install TomTom):\nMakro 1: [b][object=345446][/b] (to be blown to summon the rare)\n[code]\n/way 25 50\n/way 27 45\n/way 28 45 next to large root\n/way 29.37 55.75\n/way 30 36 in the stalks\n/way 31 46\n/way 33.77 44.55\n/way 33.76 45.52\n/way 34.08 45.83\n/way 35 59\n/way 38.4 65.9[/code]\n\nMakro2: [b][object=345446][/b] (to be blown to summon the rare)\n[code]/way 38.70 65.66 Darkreach\n/way 39 60 at Darkreach point\n/way 41.20 71.7\n/way 44.8 19.18\n/way 50 20\n/way 55.4 55.8\n/way 57 51\n/way 58.37 61.04 inside the hut\n/way 65 29\n/way 67.82 54.68 on the small dock on the pond[/code]\n\nMakro 3: [b][npc=164547][/b] spawn location (rare)\n[code]/way 65.5 29.1 common spawn of the rainbow runestag rare\n/way 54.74 28.43\n/way 51 21[/code]\n\ngood luck :-*", "date": "2021-02-11T05:17:27-06:00", "rating": 23, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Finally just found it at 58 61 in the hut! I won't update this post any more. good luck! Used my HS to Tirna Vaal and saw it coming down the way <3", "creationdate": "2021-02-18T13:15:33-06:00", "id": 1452559, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3299973, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "JulesPaece", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Found one today which is not on the list on \"Le culte de la rive noire\" at 3:30 pm at 31 36. It might be the same as 30 36, but this one is located above the waterfall whereas 31 36 is in a littlee camp with a harp, 3 seets and two tables", "creationdate": "2021-05-21T08:37:09-05:00", "id": 1489084, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3299973, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "YdraeTeramore", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "First waypoint i went (38, 65) and there it was! thank you", "creationdate": "2021-09-14T13:17:36-05:00", "id": 1512191, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3299973, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Daragan", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "pretty sure most people use paste addon now.", "creationdate": "2021-10-28T05:41:23-05:00", "id": 1517453, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3299973, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "MrPineapple", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2021-03-13T07:34:24-06:00", 9, "JulesPaece"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 44, "id": 3303374, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "heartcrash", "body": "I did this on my druid during the first week of the xpac. I just found the horn again on an alt this evening and immediately hearthed to Tirna Vaal. To my unfortunate surprise, despite having blown the horn and seeing the chat message appear stating that the Mystic Rainbowhorn had been lured into the open, it was no where to be found. It did not spawn anywhere along its route as I traced the entire thing after having waited just north of Tirna Vaal for a bit. Beware of this possible bug.", "date": "2021-02-23T01:16:39-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2021-02-23T01:17:00-06:00", 1, "heartcrash"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 45, "id": 3307483, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "premnas", "body": "I saw the star when I was on a flight to Heart of the Forest and went and found it as soon as I landed. I didn't even know what it was for, but how do you not chase after a rare called \"Mystic Rainbowhorn\"? It was 4 am, so no one else was around and it aggroed on me, so I fought it. Had I realized it was for the soulshape, I would have sent a message out to the zone.\n\nAnyway, I was able to solo it (ilvl 195 protection paladin) easily, but it took a fairly long time (I think I was able to do 3 Avenging Wrath on it, so over 4 minutes). War Mode was off. The soulshape dropped for me.\n\nGood luck, fellow Night Fae!", "date": "2021-03-10T04:12:17-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2021-03-10T04:14:53-06:00", 1, "premnas"]}
