{"commentv2": 1, "number": 47, "id": 3308991, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Zakator", "body": "I found the horn on the other side of the zone and blew it, not realising it would spawn on the opposite side of the map. Started walking towards it and finally caught up with it outside Tirna Vaal.. only for a world quest in the area (the animacones) stop me from seeing it. I did manage to tag it though, since it spawned right at the edge of the WQ area, so I eventually got it for the achievement but didn't get any loot. Don't be like me kids, and clear out WQ's before you blow that horn!", "date": "2021-03-15T15:41:07-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 48, "id": 5181455, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "greencatspryte", "body": "Hi, lucky today and got the mystic Rainbow form. I have never found the horn, however the alert came up in General chat in orange text while I was in the Heart of the Forest that the horn had been blown. Went straight to the flightmaster and went to Tirna Vaal, Stag was right there and joined the fight (just started shooting) got the quest for the form when the stag was killed. Very lucky I suspect as I was the only alliance toon there. Not sure if the orange text it was just an area alert or addon RareScanner that the horn had been used, however, whenever you get this message, go straight to Tirna Vaal to find the Stag. In this case, he was just in the middle of TV near the flight point.", "date": "2021-05-20T03:16:18-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}}
