{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 3259967, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "TheCheat54", "body": "I am fairly certain that Ravenomous requires more than just a spawn timer in order to appear. I sat near the spot and waited over 2 hours while catching up on some Mando and other things without a spawn. After I was finished with all that, I decided to start murdering mobs in the area. Ravenomous spawned in the instant after one of my killing blows landed on the Boneweave Spiderling mobs in the area which can be crushed simply by running over them.\n\nOn this spawn, Ravenomous yelled: \"Who has left me so many juicy spiderling corpses!\". The rare flew in from the cliffs to the northeast and circled the area for nearly 3 minutes before landing and becoming attackable.\n\nThis leads me to believe that crushing a certain amount of small spiders has an increasing chance to spawn the rare. Waiting alone with no activity is not enough.", "date": "2020-11-29T02:00:02-06:00", "rating": 105, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This is the way", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T11:58:44-06:00", "id": 1414465, "rating": 21, "commentid": 3259967, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "lloskka", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Im not sure about this, Im standing here for about 2hrs and killing all kinds of mobs (enemy and neutral) and rare is not spawning. EDIT - we stomped on two packs and rare spawned. No killing, just stomping", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T13:54:17-06:00", "id": 1414577, "rating": 4, "commentid": 3259967, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Schorle", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "can confirm. ran around killing spiders at 54, 16 and he spawned after about 30-40 mins. was killing with my abilities for a bit and then switched to walking over them so im not sure which is required", "creationdate": "2020-11-29T14:46:06-06:00", "id": 1414631, "rating": 3, "commentid": 3259967, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ttazi92", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Yeah, when the WQ was in there area, he was spawning every 5 mins. There's definitely a spider-kill trigger out there.", "creationdate": "2020-12-03T13:48:35-06:00", "id": 1418527, "rating": 4, "commentid": 3259967, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "iriecolorado", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just run around mounted, smashing [url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=159901/boneweave-spiderling]Boneweave Spiderling[/url] and it will appear. Took 10 minutes", "creationdate": "2020-12-08T05:21:02-06:00", "id": 1422421, "rating": 8, "commentid": 3259967, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Railis", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-11-29T02:08:42-06:00", 3, "TheCheat54"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 3260688, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "athas", "body": "We killed some of the spiders and the little neutral spiderlings and she spawned soon after with the yell. She circled around and took about a minute to land before we could engage her.", "date": "2020-11-29T14:17:59-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I would like to confirm running over the small ones, squishing them, works!", "creationdate": "2021-02-15T02:58:46-06:00", "id": 1451561, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3260688, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "athas", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
