{"commentv2": 1, "number": 8, "id": 3270208, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "S7anP", "body": "The spiders you have to kill to spawn the rare are called [b][i][u]Boneweave Spiderling[/u][/i][/b] (have about 1k HP, not the critters). You can simply mount up and run them over, squishing them, till the rare spawns.", "date": "2020-12-08T12:19:06-06:00", "rating": 46, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Boneweave spiderlings tend to come in packs of three or four, so as you're running around and squishing, look for the groups of spiderlings rather than the loners. Also, if you squish one, the others will come after you.", "creationdate": "2021-02-07T03:09:51-06:00", "id": 1449085, "rating": 5, "commentid": 3270208, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Dorelei", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
