{"commentv2": 1, "number": 11, "id": 3293566, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "ZeldaIsAGirl", "body": "This still has to be attached to some kind of timer. I've literally been running around for 20 minutes squishing boneweave spiderlings and the boss hasn't spawned. I needed Taskmaster Xox as well, so kept going over to kill whichever Taskmaster had spawned in his place. Was able to kill three taskmasters while farming these bugs, still no Ravenomous. Corpse wasn't here when I arrived, so unsure when it spawned last unfortunately.", "date": "2021-01-22T10:38:12-06:00", "rating": 18, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "When I hit 100 kills I gave up, didn't spawn for me either.", "creationdate": "2021-03-16T12:30:13-05:00", "id": 1459080, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3293566, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "FlipFlopFantasy", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "If there's a WQ up in the area, clear it 1st. Might have just been a coincidence but killed a ton of them with no spawn, after I did the WQ only took 25.", "creationdate": "2021-04-02T00:30:01-05:00", "id": 1479794, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3293566, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "brudarek", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I just killed him. The WQ was active for me too and I had completed it before going for the rare. I didn't count but if I had to guess, it took me over 200 kills.", "creationdate": "2021-08-30T07:07:05-05:00", "id": 1510050, "rating": 1, "commentid": 3293566, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "sacoplastico", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just spawned him while I was doing the Sentries WQ and didn't finish it, so the WQ doesn't appear to matter.", "creationdate": "2021-09-17T07:49:32-05:00", "id": 1512586, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3293566, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Lucifa42", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "nah doing the wq in the area made no diference", "creationdate": "2021-10-15T09:57:20-05:00", "id": 1516079, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3293566, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Beccstah", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
