{"commentv2": 1, "number": 68, "id": 2273370, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "pherkier", "body": "I know this comment might not help some people trying to get this mount, but I got this mount and some others such invincible, mimiron, etc, rushing the raids with a bunch of 600ilvl toons in 10hc mode. And correct me if im wrong but I think the drop rate has been increased, cuz I got this mount more than twice. \r\n\r\nLvling up a new toon sounds like a lot of time playing but with heirlooms and garrison's pots exp you can reach lvl100 in no time. \r\n\r\nCan anyone confirm if this is true? Or just luck, I got a lot of low drop mounts in one day. I'm not trying to be a @#$% saying how lucky I was. Just consider lvlin a crappy toon to clean old raids for extra gold.\r\n\r\nHappy grinding :)\r\n\r\ncheck my feasts of strength achev's dates. \r\nLeng - Ragnaros - US", "date": "2015-11-08T18:01:57-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
