{"commentv2": 1, "number": 70, "id": 2355444, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "grimmtooth", "body": "Helpful reminder to those retro-raiding: you have to kill [b]all the other bosses[/b] (except the special Staff boss) in order to get the bridge to appear.  Sorry, that's the way it is. And that does mean you'll have to clear enough trash to get Shannox to show up. Sorry.", "date": "2016-07-23T00:08:33-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 71, "id": 2355647, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "wyhn", "body": "I've done all the way to heroic Ragnaros and when I got finally there he didn't appear. I think this is another early bug of 7.0.3 patch.\r\n\r\nAfter I changed the difficulty into normal he appeared.", "date": "2016-07-23T10:20:23-05:00", "rating": 19, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just want to add on to that: I swapped to Normal and he appeared, but when I swapped back to Heroic he was still gone.", "creationdate": "2016-07-30T19:55:59-05:00", "id": 955919, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2355647, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Goldsmith129", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I had the same experience - no Heroic Ragnaros. And this was the first time in Firelands on this toon, so I could check on the achievements that they were all on Heroic.", "creationdate": "2016-08-05T11:34:00-05:00", "id": 957286, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2355647, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Haupt", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Appears fixed now. Cleared all the bosses on 25H and he's here.", "creationdate": "2016-08-20T16:48:59-05:00", "id": 962066, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2355647, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Steelforge", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just tried it today, and I got the same behavior described above: no Ragnaros on Heroic, after killing all bosses on Heroic, but he shows up when swapping to Normal. However, tried this on 10H, not 25H. Maybe the bug is only on 10H, and not 25H?", "creationdate": "2016-08-25T20:45:06-05:00", "id": 963259, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2355647, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Glanestel", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just happened on 25H. No Ragnaros. Switched to normal he appears. Switched back to Heroic, he disappears. Ended up killing him on normal.", "creationdate": "2016-10-03T07:58:11-05:00", "id": 990740, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2355647, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Graenor", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 72, "id": 2367355, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Bematic", "body": "Went in on paladin heroic 25\r\nkilled all bosses (beth'tilac - lord rhyolith - alysrazor - shannox and Baleroc in that order)\r\n\r\nOrb did not spawn bridge, went back and killed 99% of the whole raid. no bridge.\r\nDied, switched to normal, swithced back to heroic, walked out and back in to raid, reset the instance but still no bridge being spawned.\r\n\r\nAnyone have the same problem ?", "date": "2016-08-14T09:28:33-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
