{"commentv2": 1, "number": 29, "id": 335918, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "177744", "body": "inst he lvl  60 elite", "date": "2008-07-25T11:34:19-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "No he is a boss. No determined level.", "creationdate": "2008-07-25T17:36:49-05:00", "id": 40880, "rating": 6, "commentid": 335918, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arrace", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Raid Bosses are +3 levels the highest person in your party.  So that basically means that if you gather 10-15 level 70 players, Ragnaro will be equivalent to a 73 Elite, his health scales with levels, which is the reason it's quite possible you WILL wipe on him if you think \"lol 60 elite\" (that is, if you didnt wipe on the previous bosses or mob in Molten Core)", "creationdate": "2008-08-07T15:59:57-05:00", "id": 344923, "rating": 0, "commentid": 335918, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Chaoslux", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "His health is a set amount however all boss level mobs are treated 3+ levels ahead, so you need defense, hit, spellhit to be effective. His health does not scale.", "creationdate": "2008-08-13T14:09:43-05:00", "id": 43063, "rating": 24, "commentid": 335918, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Windscar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "256 propably. Shortest data type existing. (of course, 256x4=1024)", "creationdate": "2010-08-13T20:23:54-05:00", "id": 177449, "rating": 2, "commentid": 335918, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "stathisdjs", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "255 actually, which is the highest number representable by 8-bit binary (11111111).", "creationdate": "2010-08-26T21:09:19-05:00", "id": 179333, "rating": 3, "commentid": 335918, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "572665", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 30, "id": 350805, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "scyap", "body": "[b]Killed in 1 minute[/b]\r\n\r\nhttp://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-9024435764919244981", "date": "2008-08-12T09:35:53-05:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "2 man ZA is a little bit more unrealistic than . . . 40 man Rag?  People sure are quick to call out something as being a private server, but what's so outlandish about 3 healers, a tank, and 36 high dps classes taking out a 40 man boss quickly?  Edit: Comment accusing the video of being on a private server was deleted :P", "creationdate": "2008-09-27T04:18:03-05:00", "id": 351856, "rating": 5, "commentid": 350805, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "5487", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I'd like to see 40 of the fastest burst dps classes at level 80 run this. On an unrelated matter, [url=http://www.warcraftmovies.com/movieview.php?id=85521]10 DPS Karazhan[/url], by the guild <Giant Censored Robots>", "creationdate": "2008-11-06T13:56:11-06:00", "id": 358973, "rating": 4, "commentid": 350805, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Fizzles", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "8 dps, there is a bear + resto shammy.   Still fun though :)", "creationdate": "2009-03-02T18:57:25-06:00", "id": 391859, "rating": 0, "commentid": 350805, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Oomkin", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Personally pulling off a 3min kill in pre-bwl gear was the standard mark of achievement.  If you were using AQ20 gear it was acceptable as a 'gear filler' slop, but only if it didn't exceed your total by 8%.    My old guild nearly got it, we only missed the mark by 3 seconds.  We were happy with the attempt, if a few people didn't die early we would have had it.  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Oa1Qux2GWA", "creationdate": "2009-04-17T17:10:40-05:00", "id": 400383, "rating": 1, "commentid": 350805, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "elilla", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
