{"commentv2": 1, "number": 34, "id": 435276, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "222832", "body": "\"By fire be purged!\"\n/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Ragnaros\\\\RagnarosSpecialAttack01.wav\")\n\n\"Taste the flames of Sulfuron!\"\n/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Ragnaros\\\\RagnarosSpecialAttack02.wav\")\n\n\"My patience is dwindling! Come, gnats, to your death!\"\n/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Ragnaros\\\\RagnarosSpecialAttack03.wav\")\n\n\"Die, insects!\"\n/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Ragnaros\\\\RagnarosSlay01.wav\")\n\nNasty sounds( Aka raggy dies):\n/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Ragnaros\\\\RagnarosDeath.wav\")\n\nJust a few scripts i could find ;P\nHave fun with em^^ (Feel free to add more)", "date": "2008-11-08T11:22:32-06:00", "rating": 88, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thanks; ) Editted.", "creationdate": "2009-02-04T11:40:47-06:00", "id": 385946, "rating": 0, "commentid": 435276, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "222832", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "To hear this in game all you do is copy the text and then paste it in the chat box by pressing Ctrl-V (or Cmd-V for Macs) and it should play.", "creationdate": "2009-07-11T22:20:54-05:00", "id": 109167, "rating": 25, "commentid": 435276, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "288482", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Don't take it as a stupid question but is there a way if i could ringtone them to my phone?", "creationdate": "2011-07-13T14:25:56-05:00", "id": 252142, "rating": 4, "commentid": 435276, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ukkan", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Use a program to unpack the .mpqs (Might violate Blizzes ToS/be against the law) and just follow that directory. Extract the .wav and toss it on your phone. Bada-bing. Might even be able to open it up with WinRar.", "creationdate": "2011-09-05T01:21:12-05:00", "id": 262574, "rating": 4, "commentid": 435276, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "CellPunk", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "\"BY FIRE BE PURGED! BY FIRE BE PURGED!\" \"What the **** was that?!\" \"My cell phone.\"", "creationdate": "2012-04-22T12:54:23-05:00", "id": 537829, "rating": 3, "commentid": 435276, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "lunayah", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-02-04T11:40:33-06:00", 1, "222832"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 35, "id": 441173, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "Teradon", "body": "Would he be solo able for a lvl 80 druid?\nI would like to do this run a lot, as I'm looking for \"The eye of Sulfarac\".", "date": "2008-11-13T13:45:43-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I also managed to do it as a Prot Pala and BM hunter combo. Nothing special gear wise, both been 80 for only a few days, mostly instance blues from leveling up and the odd crafted epic.  Just some things I done to make the fight easyer  - used 300 fire res including aura - used wisdom instead of Sanc for Rag, switching to Sanc for adds and then back again - kept 1-3 mobs alive during the add phase to return me to full mana, killed them when rag returns - used judgement of light, this alone kept the pet up which was very resistant to his knockback - postioned myself so when I got knocked back I", "creationdate": "2008-11-13T13:45:44-06:00", "id": 389042, "rating": 5, "commentid": 441173, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "324587", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just did him on my prot paladinn 413FR with a hunter friend. Was just going to walk out of the knockbacks but after pet died, he just waited and didn't seem to do the knockback untill I moved back to melee range, so I guess someone has to be in melee range for him to use it. The Magma Blast from not being in melee range and the whole dmg in general was pretty pitiful, just keep Sacred up, use SoL + JoL and I recommend only ShoR. He hits slow so you get really no mana from BoSanc. When Sons come, just try to heal up as much as possible, they don't hit hard and are level 60 so they're no threat,", "creationdate": "2008-11-13T13:45:44-06:00", "id": 385719, "rating": 3, "commentid": 441173, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Artharas", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Solo'd him (and all of MC) as a resto druid. I'm ulduar 10-man hard modes geared. No FR gear, just Mark of the Wild and a [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=44939]Lesser Flask of Resistance[/url], altho I admit it wasnt necessary.  There's 2 ways to do it: either melee him for procs of Omen of Clarity, or just do it ranged (as I did).  1- Melee I noticed that I needed to heal myself a lot more when I meleed him, and there's the knockback. As a pally suggested, face him SE, so you can land on the top of the rock.  2- Ranged He will keep attacking you with Magma Blast, but with the small resistan", "creationdate": "2008-11-13T13:45:44-06:00", "id": 418341, "rating": 3, "commentid": 441173, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "246648", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The instance is on a multi-day reset timer. I think there's plenty enough time to douse the flames.", "creationdate": "2008-12-02T08:53:25-06:00", "id": 366140, "rating": 2, "commentid": 441173, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Tresjin", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "In 3.0.8: \"You no longer need quintessence to summon Majordomo Executus.\"", "creationdate": "2008-12-17T16:15:03-06:00", "id": 65601, "rating": 19, "commentid": 441173, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "vexis58", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-12-21T17:13:34-06:00", 1, "Teradon"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 36, "id": 469507, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Azvolrien", "body": "His name is an allusion to Ragnarok, the end of the world in Norse mythology. Having never set foot in Molten Core, that's all I can add to this entry.", "date": "2008-11-25T12:07:26-06:00", "rating": 74, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I think Azvolrien is right about ragnaros being a reference to ragnarok, the end of the world. I also belive his appaerence may be a referance to Surt, a fire giant who at ragnarok would swing his flaming sword over his head and thereby setting the entire world aflame.", "creationdate": "2009-04-03T11:14:04-05:00", "id": 397651, "rating": 2, "commentid": 469507, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "320146", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "In Swedish Mythology it's \"Ragnar\u00f6k\" :)", "creationdate": "2011-03-22T14:52:22-05:00", "id": 482003, "rating": 3, "commentid": 469507, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Shoto", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "now it's a spell of the second last boss in Halls of Valor (Valhalla?)", "creationdate": "2016-08-12T16:45:52-05:00", "id": 959757, "rating": 0, "commentid": 469507, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ikechi", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
