{"commentv2": 1, "number": 50, "id": 649628, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "187014", "body": "Extremely time consuming to solo on a prot paladin but nothing particularly difficult about him.  Keep sacred shield up at all times, JoW/Seal of wisdom.  Wore roughly 330 FR with aura, make sure you bring backup weapons, he will easily break one of them over the course of the fight.  Pop all of your cds immediately after sons are down, should have avenging wrath up after every sons phase.", "date": "2009-03-20T21:03:34-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
