{"commentv2": 1, "number": 52, "id": 656127, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "265607", "body": "Is this soloable by a ret pally, or maybe two mannable with a healer? Onyxia is really too easy atm so i was looking for something new to try out :) Didn't want to take all that time to get to him just to find out he isn't...", "date": "2009-03-26T08:56:29-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The phase when you fight Ragnaros can be soloed by a well-geared and skilled retri pala. But when he submerges and you got to fight all his sons of flame, you'll have serious trouble as retribution. I tried it one time, they simply hit too much to be able to survive without a shield. Spec prot and kill him :) That's what I did :)", "creationdate": "2009-04-15T01:01:35-05:00", "id": 399680, "rating": 0, "commentid": 656127, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "279763", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
