{"commentv2": 1, "number": 119, "id": 1266183, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "9945_", "body": "Soloed him as an 85 Enhancement Shaman today. Only tricky part was dealing with his various knockbacks. Try to position yourself so that you get knockbacked into one of the rock formations around him, and keep pets, summons etc. out at all time so they can soak up some knockbacks as well.", "date": "2010-12-29T14:50:40-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
