{"commentv2": 1, "number": 128, "id": 1322880, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "752869", "body": "Solo'd as a 85 Frost Mage. This is a really straight forward fight for a frost mage. I popped mirror images at the beginning and never got knocked back he died in 48 seconds. Just use deep freeze on CD and pop coldsnap to get two DF off early.", "date": "2011-02-05T16:34:36-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Very easy fight for a Frost Mage. His damage is so negligible that I decided to take some screenshots of his attacks against me.  The knockback should be no concern to any mage as you can just blink right back to the ground.", "creationdate": "2011-02-16T13:21:54-06:00", "id": 225632, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1322880, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "545765", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 129, "id": 1327409, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Kiruvi", "body": "Solo'd as an 85 Fury Warrior (ilvl 335) last week. The only challenge is his knockback which does about 35-45% damage; however, I think that if one were to stand so that were knocked into the lava this wouldn't be a problem, making him a fairly easy fight. Will be doing him again tonight with ilvl 342 and the above-mentioned strategy, will report back on how it goes.", "date": "2011-02-08T17:43:31-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
