{"commentv2": 1, "number": 160, "id": 1455021, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "767367", "body": "Confirmed he can spawn twice in 4.2 if you die once, then run back and kill him I think. Just happened for me.\r\n\r\nhttp://img148.imageshack.us/img148/5600/2ragspawns.jpg\r\n\r\nI just killed him on my DK,  I forgot to stand in the right spot the first time and I died from falling damage. After running back, killing him, and looting - I suddenly noticed that Majordomo was standing there staring at me. Talked to Domo, and wouldn't you know it,  another Rag spawned ontop of the first Rag corpse.\r\n\r\nI'm wondering if I purposely died on the 2nd Rag spawn, and went back and killed him just like the first. If a third Ragnaros would spawn, and so-forth... Hmmm guess I'll have to try on my other 85 sometime.", "date": "2011-06-30T01:04:19-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Confirmed - Same exact thing happened to me. Stood in the wrong spot, died during the first fight and summoned another Ragnaros after I killed him the first time. Totally trying this again next week to see if you can't just resummon him over and over, or just once.  *Edit* Seems Blizzard fixed this bug. A couple of people also got banned for using this bug, which was termed as exploitation. Just goes to show that yes, sometimes you SHOULD look a gift horse in the mouth.", "creationdate": "2011-07-01T18:57:56-05:00", "id": 487436, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1455021, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kasa24", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Thx a lot! [u]I tried to wait for 3rd spawn[/u] of Majordomo. I did following things: talked to Majordomo, engaged in combat with Ragnaros and successfully died, then came to Ragnaros room and waited till Majordomo spawns. It took 5-7 mins or so for 2nd spawn. I repeated actions above and [u]waited about 15 mins for 3rd spawn but unfortunately he didn't showed up[/u]. IDK whether Ragna despawns after 30 mins or less or doesn't despawn at all, since I need an eye I used my chance :D If someone have more patience that me please post you results!", "creationdate": "2011-07-03T08:14:48-05:00", "id": 487541, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1455021, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "kolbaska", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
