{"commentv2": 1, "number": 193, "id": 1785244, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "WarlockHunter30", "body": "I am wondering, is it possible to just have one player in your group sitting in Stormwind while you are just in the raid, slaughtering everything, even trash? Will the other player get to roll on loot? I hope not. I am asking because I have a lv 89, almost lv 90, hunter, who so dearly wants to get tier 1 hunter gear to transmog and also to get transmog Dragonbreath Hand Cannon.", "date": "2012-12-21T18:53:24-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Not outside the zone, no.", "creationdate": "2013-01-06T22:54:40-06:00", "id": 620030, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1785244, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "nosf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You no longer need to be in a raid group to enter old raids.", "creationdate": "2013-03-10T03:16:09-05:00", "id": 639872, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1785244, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "digitalutopia1", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "How aboput the new ones?", "creationdate": "2014-03-21T00:04:25-05:00", "id": 735866, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1785244, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "daaani", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-12-21T18:58:49-06:00", 2, "WarlockHunter30"]}
