{"commentv2": 1, "number": 197, "id": 1946436, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Iwannabeer", "body": "As already noted (much earlier in these comments) Raggy is probably named for the Norse myth Ragnarok: the epic battle between Thor, Loki, Odin and pretty much all of the old gods who will destroy each other and plunge the world back into the sea - killing us all. The Jorvik Viking Center predicted it would occur on February 22, 2014. Apparently Ragnarok has about as much credibility as the end of the Mayan calendar so... see ya in Azeroth fellow Wowheads! :)", "date": "2014-02-24T16:24:47-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 198, "id": 1952406, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Takata", "body": "Surprisingly soloed him very easily with my lvl 90 prot warrior. Only thing I had to worry about was his knockback,\"wrath of Ragnaros\" which is his knockback ability. It didn't do much damage but the fall damage did, damaged me for just over 300k hp. Luckily I had just killed him and he was down to about 20% health when he did it and he died just as I was in the air. His hp drops pretty fast so I think anyone with a decently geared 90 can solo the whole instance easily.", "date": "2014-03-20T14:05:49-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "A decently geared, bursting destro lock can 1-shot him with a 2 mil Chaos Bolt.", "creationdate": "2014-08-06T13:47:32-05:00", "id": 762861, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1952406, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "trollneverreroll", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
