{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 407730, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Bleach", "body": "Found one in TB after 3.0.2 went live, and attacked it on my combat rogue for 10 minutes.\r\n\r\nI don't wanna post any numbers because of the recent patch, but I was glancing and missing yellow attacks on this thing (my hit rating was well over 80). Either this thing is level 83 or the battle mechanics changed a lot in 3.0.2 .\r\n\r\nI haven't tried to skill up weapons on these yet.", "date": "2008-10-16T04:59:03-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 408044, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "mofunz", "body": "Im nearly positive that this dummy is a lvl83+", "date": "2008-10-16T10:37:08-05:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It is, because he has slightly less than 1M more HP than Brutallus and takes much longer than six minutes to kill. The Dummy should berserk and start killing people in the town. :)", "creationdate": "2008-11-09T23:05:50-06:00", "id": 55241, "rating": 22, "commentid": 408044, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "jarhad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It is indeed level 83, I tested it with exactly capped hit rating for 30 minutes and not a single attack missed. And by the way, they do not die. I got mine down from 11 million health to 1 health...and the damn thing would not die.", "creationdate": "2009-01-01T18:25:37-06:00", "id": 69407, "rating": 3, "commentid": 408044, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Beetroot", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "They're labeled as \"Boss\" mobs. Boss mobs always count as your character's level + 3 (so a Boss mob to a level 22 would count as a level 25 mob).", "creationdate": "2009-01-26T21:06:03-06:00", "id": 383786, "rating": 5, "commentid": 408044, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "146819", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "except as a hit capped 70 mage i couldn't touch it. at all.  regular bosses do indeed count as 3 levels higher than you no matter what you are, but this dummy really does appear to be different.", "creationdate": "2009-02-01T20:33:24-06:00", "id": 77220, "rating": 17, "commentid": 408044, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arbron", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "the dummy is lvl 83. \"boss\" doesn't mean +3 to your level...cuz if you went into Onyxia (63), Karazhan (73) and Obsidian Sanctum (83). The \"boss\" just designates what it is, a boss. So ya, you can be hit cap'd at 60, 70, 27, etc. but you will have no chance unless you are lvl 80.", "creationdate": "2009-04-20T01:22:20-05:00", "id": 400873, "rating": 1, "commentid": 408044, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "55601", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 408326, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Isurus", "body": "Dont try to kill him, His http://www.wowitemcreator.com/view/270062/Sucky_Plywood_Shield.html\r\nand http://www.wowitemcreator.com/view/270065/Wooden_Sword.html wont drop. We were around 100 people there, from lv 1-70. Nuking this bastard. Took almost 7 hours. He had 100k life. And by the fact he is like lv 83 - we missed alot. Everybody were shouting \"Heroic Training Dummy - World First!\" and \"Enrage timer coming up!\" \"Flame Wreath inc - DONT MOVE\". But then he was there. With 1 hp. We couldn't kill him.", "date": "2008-10-16T14:53:11-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The fact that your raid leader rallied so many morons for attacking a TRAINING DUMMY for that long is impressive (and very very very very very stupid)", "creationdate": "2008-11-17T05:25:14-06:00", "id": 361289, "rating": -1, "commentid": 408326, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "170735", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 409978, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "EnDsInRuBy", "body": "This is to test out your dps/new gear what ever you want on. This thing is equivalent to a WotLK boss so you know what you would be hitting a boss for.", "date": "2008-10-17T20:44:39-05:00", "rating": 29, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I'd suggest using an addon such as recount while doing this to get an accurate picture of your non raid-buffed DPS.", "creationdate": "2009-01-09T07:29:02-06:00", "id": 71423, "rating": 18, "commentid": 409978, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "262277", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 8, "id": 412427, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Nayson", "body": "Ranged have been testing their DPS on [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=20284#comments]Dr Boom![/url] pretty much since everybody hit 70. \r\nThere have been tons of suggestions that Blizz should incorporate this into the game properly, not only so that melee can join in the DPS tests but people on PvP servers can try stuff without getting ganked, that its easy to break combat and walk away when you are through and that you dont have to travel all the way to Area 52 when you want to try out a new talent build/spell rotation/piece of gear. \r\n\r\nThe Target Dummy is what was asked for.  Reset your damage meters and let rip.", "date": "2008-10-19T18:37:20-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 417125, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Ryxis", "body": "'m rather annoyed they added a level 60 one, a level 70 and a level 83, wheres the level 73 for us to test dps versus current raid bosses?", "date": "2008-10-23T04:12:59-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "To mofunz also. Level ? Boss is always three (3) levels abow you what comes to hitting and stuff, so this should and would and could be the only training dummy you'll ever need.", "creationdate": "2008-10-26T14:02:47-05:00", "id": 356949, "rating": 6, "commentid": 417125, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Nari", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "level ? is also a mob 10 levels or more above you  i beat on the level ? dummy with my mage, who is hit capped and almost every single hit was resisted, either i had an incredibly bad string of luck or the dummy is level 80+ (likely to be 83, lich king raid boss)", "creationdate": "2008-10-29T05:15:44-05:00", "id": 357409, "rating": 2, "commentid": 417125, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ryxis", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Wrong Mr. Nari, these are level 83, not just three levels higher then you. I found myself missing far more then I would for this to be just three levels higher then me. Just take a lowbie alt there and see how much you hit it.", "creationdate": "2009-01-01T16:49:19-06:00", "id": 376595, "rating": 0, "commentid": 417125, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "drewidice", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
