{"commentv2": 1, "number": 14, "id": 485025, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Sly99", "body": "As of now, they do not lose any health, at least in SW, no matter how much you hit it for, seeing as its health is around 500 I think, a 1k crit would theoretically destroy it. These are mostly meant for testing out abilities / specs and damage logging. They are considered level 80. They have a horde, and alliance flag respectivley for the opposite faction. They are affected by all debuffs also.", "date": "2008-12-02T12:55:35-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 15, "id": 489698, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "38803", "body": "The wowhead data for this heroic training dummy seems to indicate that it can be found in Dalaran, but I cannot find it at the indicated location either above ground or below.  I suspect that this was present in beta and was removed in the live game but the removal was not reflected in the wowhead database.\r\n\r\nI certainly wish there was one (or many of them) in Dalaran as I hate having to travel to Orgrimmar to test out a new item.", "date": "2008-12-04T14:07:44-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 16, "id": 509920, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "220928", "body": "Yeah, I wouldn't trust this thing. Ding'd 80, and went to test my dps as an enh shammy.\n\nLong story short, it's Glancing Blow mechanic is calculated as if it was 87, *NOT* 83.\n\nMechanics: 10 + Mob Defense (lvl * 5) - Your Defense = % Chance to Glance.\nUsing my stats: 10 + 415 - 398 = 27% chance to glance against lvl 73\n\nActual glancing chance recorded from a 1250 attack sample:  46.37%\n\nReversing this result:\n\n47* = 10 + X - 398\n47 - 10 + 398 = X\n435 = X\n435 / 5 = Mob's level, Mob's level = 87.\n\nAgain, *NOT* reliable, unless all bosses are now treated as level 87. At least for melee..", "date": "2008-12-14T16:14:52-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-12-15T00:15:03-06:00", 2, "220928"]}
