{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 569376, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "153623", "body": "For the love of god!  \r\n[b]First[/b]: These cannot level your weapon skill.\r\n[b]Secondly[/b]: Blizzard tried to make these as realistic as possible, meaning.... Hmmmm... Where should a melee damage dealer stand?  \r\n     Learn to play your class, so stand behind the mob you are attacking to reduce the chance of getting blocked, dodged, and parried (go wowwiki and read about expertise).\r\n[small][b]Thirdly[/b]: Learn the tactics, and be careful! These dummies are VERY destructive. You must never stand at the side where he holds his sword, and run away from it as SOON as he starts staring at you.[/small]", "date": "2009-01-19T11:23:07-06:00", "rating": 37, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "In my experience of what is 'real' no training dummy has ever managed to block, parry or dodge an attack that I've made on it.", "creationdate": "2009-02-07T16:36:25-06:00", "id": 386750, "rating": 0, "commentid": 569376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Evilhealbot", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Yes, I know...", "creationdate": "2009-02-08T05:27:35-06:00", "id": 386863, "rating": 0, "commentid": 569376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Evilhealbot", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Standing behind a mob has no effect on its Dodge chance, FYI.", "creationdate": "2009-08-20T12:28:24-05:00", "id": 117406, "rating": 7, "commentid": 569376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "AudreyChandler", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Actually, when I was messing around on my paladin I