{"commentv2": 1, "number": 28, "id": 738276, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "364012", "body": "The talent Necrosis doesn't seem to function properly against dummies. Anyone else having this malfunction?", "date": "2009-06-05T18:25:21-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I've found Unholy Blight (the DoT), wandering plague and necrosis to only work against the boss dummy in Orgimmar, and haven't found another working dummy. Maybe the alliance dummies work.  Edit: By don't work, i mean they only do 1 damage.", "creationdate": "2009-11-07T20:49:42-06:00", "id": 131241, "rating": 0, "commentid": 738276, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "oppewala", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Necrosis, Blood Caked Blade and Unholy Blight don't overkill, so when the dummy has 1 health, they will hit for 1.  If the dummy has 10mil health, you will do normal damage with these abilities.", "creationdate": "2010-02-09T21:43:57-06:00", "id": 148232, "rating": 1, "commentid": 738276, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Voldar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
