{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2335653, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "leobolin", "body": "She is now located in Bladefist Bay outside Orgrimmar in 7.0 while preparing for the Broken Shore scenario. Note that she is only there [i]before[/i] you complete the scenario. She sells items that were previously only available during patch 5.3:\n[ul][li][item=97901][/li]\n[li][item=97919][/li]\n[li][item=97942][/li]\n[li][item=98552][/li][/ul]\n\nShe is intended for Horde players only according to a recent tweet by Muffinus:\n\n[quote]Horde-only, along with Fo'rum. Alliance get Lucky Items vendor and Alaina's Bonnet.[/quote]\nhttps://twitter.com/Muffinus/status/763165150304055297\n\nHowever, all items are account wide and can be used by Alliance characters too if you unlock them on a Horde character.\n\nThe similar (but less interesting) Alliance NPC is [npc=2795].", "date": "2016-05-30T09:38:18-05:00", "rating": 69, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "She stands at Bladefist Bay, right before the docks.", "creationdate": "2016-06-16T17:34:17-05:00", "id": 947197, "rating": 6, "commentid": 2335653, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Karadine", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I checked for her on multiple alliance toons and neither Ravika nor her tents were there. I checked on toons that have completed broken shore, were in progress for broken shore, and toons that havent started it. I am not entirely sure how I can interact with the NPC if she isnt there.", "creationdate": "2016-08-09T18:42:13-05:00", "id": 958453, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2335653, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DominarQuintus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The new Lenny is at 28,27 to the left of the first main dock.", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T00:23:42-05:00", "id": 958557, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2335653, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Stevenzb", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You can't, she's not available to Alliance. You use a Horde alt to buy from her.", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T12:14:23-05:00", "id": 958789, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2335653, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Saliira", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Coords for here are 55, 11 for her, just in front of the main dock", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T14:43:10-05:00", "id": 958853, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2335653, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Unforgvn", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-08-10T19:23:23-05:00", 21, "leobolin"]}
