{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 2364064, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Ketsuki", "body": "A few things about this NPC. \n\n-She will NOT appear for Demon Hunters\n-She will NOT appear if you already did the Broken Shore scenario.\n-She will NOT sell to Alliance. \nYou need to buy these toys on a character that hasn't done that scenario.", "date": "2016-08-09T19:17:10-05:00", "rating": 87, "indent": 0, "roles": 258, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "she will NOT sell to Alliance.", "creationdate": "2016-08-09T22:41:13-05:00", "id": 958529, "rating": 13, "commentid": 2364064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Purgatorywolf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "responseroles": "16", "responseuser": "Ketsuki", "response": "", "lastEdit": ["2016-08-10T14:00:52-05:00", 1, "Ketsuki"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 2364067, "nreplies": 12, "sticky": 0, "user": "FrostKittyPaw", "body": "Update: As of patch 7.1, she can also be found on the Echo Isles in Durotar.\n\nShe stands by the large pile of horde crates next to the Bladefist Bay by Orgrimmar. She is visible during the pre-legion event before departing for the Broken Shore. After the Broken Shore event, she can be found on the Echo Isles in Durotar. As @Ketsuki noted, Demon Hunters can not do the Broken Shore quest line, so they can not see this version of the npc.\nShe sells the following for small amounts of gold (50g or less). These items were only available during the Darkspear Rebellion event (patch 5.3). These items unlock on an account wide basis and can be used by both factions.\n[ul]\n[li][item=97901][/li]\n[li][item=97919][/li]\n[li][item=97942][/li]\n[li][item=98552][/li]\n[/ul]\n\nThe horde also gets a second vendor, [npc=113151], who is nearby Ravika at the bay. He sells three different one-time-use posts that stack in unique stacks of 20. Beware, rumor says this troll loves to hang out around the official WoW forums!\n[ul]\n[li][item=141318][/li][/li]\n[li][item=141319][/li][/li]\n[li][item=141320][/li][/li]\n[/ul]\n\nThe Alliance equivalent is [npc=108533] at the Stormwind Harbor (28,27) who sells the following prior to embarking to the Broken Shore. The NPC is also available to alliance players at the Old Town in Stormwind ([npc=2795]). The lucky shirt appears exclusive to the event and is unique. I haven't noticed any special effects from the charms.\n[ul]\n[li][item=97921][/li]\n[li][item=138385][/li]\n[li][item=138383] (Stacks to 20.)[/li]\n[li][item=138382] (Stacks to 20.)[/li]\n[li][item=138384] (Stacks to 20. Not to be confused with [item=5373], or cereal. Please do NOT eat this item!)[/li]\n[/ul]\n\nFor more hidden Legion event items (such as [item=139389]/[item=139391]) check out this WoWhead guide:\n[guide=4177]\n\nFor hidden demon hunter starting items (such as [item=129192]/[item=129195]) check out this WoWhead guide:\n[guide=3930]", "date": "2016-08-09T19:19:37-05:00", "rating": 186, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Seems fair and unbiased.", "creationdate": "2016-08-09T20:26:16-05:00", "id": 958491, "rating": 83, "commentid": 2364067, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Spazticated", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Jeremy Feasel says she is NOT accessible to Alliance.", "creationdate": "2016-08-09T22:40:57-05:00", "id": 958528, "rating": 17, "commentid": 2364067, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Purgatorywolf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "On the french comments part Cleclestria said that you can found the NPC on echo isles at 57.51 - 62.42 (in front of Vol'jin House)", "creationdate": "2016-11-17T17:07:32-06:00", "id": 1009687, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2364067, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 16384, "username": "Petitgreen", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "adding to \"Update: As of patch 7.1, she can also be found on the Echo Isles in Durotar.\" is that its about /way 57.5 62.4 for ravika or near the huts witht hte horde flag", "creationdate": "2017-01-06T11:25:27-06:00", "id": 1021969, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2364067, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "noctusmirus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "holdem you are dead wrong. You need something. There is some sort of requirement because myself, and many others here are not seeing her in ANY of the locations where she is apparently supposed to be. I logged onto my level 89 or 88 druid and she was not in either place. But I logged into my level 100 horde that hasn't done any of the Legion stuff yet, and she was ONLY at the Echo Isle location. She was NOT in the other location in the northern part of Durotar", "creationdate": "2017-01-29T09:26:25-06:00", "id": 1028912, "rating": 5, "commentid": 2364067, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Soundfx4", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-12-30T14:11:33-06:00", 11, "FrostKittyPaw"]}
