{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 2364441, "nreplies": 10, "sticky": 0, "user": "overlateralus", "body": "This is ridiculous. I was hyped on that quest and walk through to ship for saving Azeroth. Now Blizzard telling me that i can not obtain the toy because i did my job. Not fair at all.", "date": "2016-08-10T07:56:45-05:00", "rating": 127, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "@jasiek And if you don't have a level 100 alt? You get completely boned. I hope for the sake of everyone they allow these \"hidden\" items to be obtainable during Legion.", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T11:54:11-05:00", "id": 958783, "rating": 16, "commentid": 2364441, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Zaydene", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "My thoughts exactly, I had ONE horde alt. so now if I want those items I have to speed level an alt to get them before they are gone, meanwhile not being able to do invasions or any other work on the rest of my toons.. Frustrated doesn't cover it.", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T17:03:23-05:00", "id": 958921, "rating": 19, "commentid": 2364441, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Purgatorywolf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Except that Demon Hunters cannot participate in the Broken Shore cenario because timeline-wise it takes place at the same time as their intro questline.", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T17:27:27-05:00", "id": 958933, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2364441, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Mightyena5875345", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I was lagging so badly I could barely see the quest items, much less look around for fun vendors. So now I'm doing hellfire ramparts with three other level 60-ish DKs!", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T22:56:59-05:00", "id": 959028, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2364441, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Adelline", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "@bleak101 And for those of us who boosted an Alliance toon because we didn't know there would be temporary faction-locked content?", "creationdate": "2016-08-11T00:06:38-05:00", "id": 959043, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2364441, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "voodoopimp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 2364822, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "tabitreader", "body": "Blizzard and Wowhead should have made us more aware of a secret vendor LONG before I took my only 100 Horde on the Broken Shore questline without a care in the world to look out for a secret vendor!\r\n\r\nKnowledge is power! Wowhead is so good at these kinds of things, and now my only option is to power level a death knight on another realm from 55-98 in less than 19 days.  Ouch.", "date": "2016-08-10T17:32:49-05:00", "rating": 37, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "\"More aware of secret vendor\".. Hows that secret?", "creationdate": "2016-08-11T06:19:21-05:00", "id": 959162, "rating": 6, "commentid": 2364822, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "puskaryssa", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Well, there was no LOUD INFO that we shoudl be careful that this vendor will appear and sell removed toys AND be available only before doing quest chain and unavailable after You complete it. So I agree it's a secret vendor.", "creationdate": "2016-08-11T06:30:04-05:00", "id": 959167, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2364822, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Evenuel", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The return of the 5.3 toys was announced a while ago when beta testing was still in progress. It was announced both on forums (with description how to access the vendor) and here on wowhead, thus you could have prepared for it. If you missed it it's your own fault...Unless you want to be spoon-fed while playing the game", "creationdate": "2016-08-12T05:51:03-05:00", "id": 959574, "rating": -11, "commentid": 2364822, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Skunkwalker", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Alot of people started playing again when the pre patch hit so that\u00b4s not really fair to say.", "creationdate": "2016-08-12T08:11:43-05:00", "id": 959599, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2364822, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Roadhouse", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "As of 3/10/17, this still works! Thanks very much ;-)", "creationdate": "2017-03-10T17:41:52-06:00", "id": 1036712, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2364822, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "BowWow", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 11, "id": 2364949, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "Wolfwings", "body": "IF YOU HAVE BOOSTED A HORDE CHARACTER- You will appear in the broken shore scenario. BUT... you can still get to this vendor. You need to:\n\n- Use your Garrison Hearthstone right away on the boat. [Normal HS may work now, was previously broken]\n- Take your Garrison Portal to Warspear -> Org [Edit: You can find yoru portal in the tower just outside your side gate of your Garrison's 'ring']\n- Find a Hero's Call Board and accept the newest quest on the bottom\n- Walk down the path towards the docks to this NPC to get your items!\n- Winner!", "date": "2016-08-10T22:29:29-05:00", "rating": 28, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I also got trapped after using my hearthstone but after logging into another character and back into that character I became unstuck.", "creationdate": "2016-08-10T23:07:56-05:00", "id": 959032, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2364949, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kuipo", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I just tried on another character and I can confirm this works. But I used my normal hearthstone and didn't get stuck.", "creationdate": "2016-08-11T07:19:20-05:00", "id": 959183, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2364949, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Fauxfur", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Actually there is an even easier way. When you are on the boat simply leave the group, it will port you out and you'll be standing on the docks at Orgrimmar not far from the vendor.", "creationdate": "2016-08-11T09:48:24-05:00", "id": 959229, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2364949, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Catweazle", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I boosted and followed this up to the part where I was supposed to take a portal to Org from the garrison. After running around for about half an hour I could not for the life of me find any portal there, even tried googling. In the end I just used my hearthstone to Org. Think maybe you could edit this mini guide to describe where the portal is so players who never played WoD can find it?", "creationdate": "2016-08-13T02:18:12-05:00", "id": 959877, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2364949, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "PhoenixUnity07", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You can also leave the broken shore scenario like you leave any instance by right click and choose leave instance and it will port you back to Org. Don't have to go through all the porting and flying.", "creationdate": "2016-08-14T11:24:14-05:00", "id": 960303, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2364949, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "lovelywaz", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-08-14T01:06:12-05:00", 3, "Wolfwings"]}
