{"commentv2": 1, "number": 16, "id": 2365658, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "DrPanda187", "body": "So, question.\n\nIs she only going to be there for now in the pre-launch event, or will she be available after Legion to anyone who hasn't completed the Broken Shore quest on Horde-side?\n\nI ask this because I would really like to get this, but I don't want to have to boost a character just to do it before Legion hits. If I can take my time and level a fresh 100 Horde character during Legion in order to get the item, that would be much better.", "date": "2016-08-11T23:14:37-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I am in the same situation so does anyone know the answer to this?", "creationdate": "2016-08-12T08:39:08-05:00", "id": 959609, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2365658, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "CyberBlade", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "She (and the totem guy) are visible to any toon with the broken shore quest, even after Legion has launched.", "creationdate": "2016-10-27T13:37:23-05:00", "id": 1001826, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2365658, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Purgatorywolf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-08-11T23:15:10-05:00", 1, "DrPanda187"]}
