{"commentv2": 1, "number": 19, "id": 2366780, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "karioth", "body": "I put in a ticket to see if it was intended for the vendor to only be available during an unusually narrow window and recieved this response:\n\n\"Game Master XXX here!  Thanks for hanging on while I take a look at this for you.  \n\nI hate to be the bearer of bad news on this one, but yes.  Ravika is only available *before* doing the Broken Shores scenario.  We always want to help players out whenever the game is not working properly, but in this case everything is actually working as intended.  So, I\u2019m afraid that we will not be able to bring her back or provide any of the items that she sells.\n\nIf you want to see this changed, though, we definitely want to hear it!  Unfortunately, though, we GMs actually don\u2019t have the ability to make changes to the game like that  The best way to do this is through the \u201cSubmit Suggestion\u201d option from the in-game help menu.  This will send your suggestion straight to the developers so they can consider it and work on adding it to the game.  I would also recommend taking to the forums.  If you can get a good discussion going about a change you\u2019d like to see, then they will take notice and get it added.\"\n\nI would recommend that everyone who got screwed over follow this exact advice of submitting a suggestion via the in-game tool. If they get enough noise about it Ravika might just show up again.   :)", "date": "2016-08-13T10:56:00-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-08-13T11:58:04-05:00", 2, "karioth"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 2366955, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "jayne9878", "body": "I went to Bladefist Bay on my level 98 horde and I could not see Ravika. So I pushed to 100. Still nothing. Make sure you pick up [url=http://www.wowhead.com/quest=43926/the-legion-returns]The Legion Returns[/url] quest so the phased area shows up. If the quest doesn't pop up for you after you level (like it did on my existing level 100 toons), you can pick it up from the command board.", "date": "2016-08-13T18:15:00-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 21, "id": 2368989, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Blizky", "body": "Ravika is only visible during the quest The Legion Returns (43926). This quest is not part of the Legion pre-release events and will be available in game for any horde reaching level 100 indefinably.\r\n\r\nSo don\u2019t worry in having to get those toys and transmog before Legion release.", "date": "2016-08-16T15:07:58-05:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Two days after legion's launch I can confirm the alliance equivalent of this vendor still exists in game and can be interacted with on a lvl 100, non demon hunter, character that has not completed the starter broken isles chain. Once you level your next horde to 100, make sure to pick up the quest from the command board and buy her toys before shipping out.", "creationdate": "2016-08-28T13:35:03-05:00", "id": 963873, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2368989, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "mgdimarc", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 22, "id": 2369755, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "ToviValdora", "body": "I don't have Horde toons anymore so I made a level one orc, mailed her two [item=69210]s, ran her to Ravika, bought all four items, then mailed the extra gold to some random lowbie in Durotar.", "date": "2016-08-17T17:27:23-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "could you explain more? how can you see that npc withput the quests that is for level 100 and what does the tabards has to do with it? ty", "creationdate": "2016-08-18T12:17:22-05:00", "id": 961503, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2369755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Blizky", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You can mail guild tabards across characters, factions and even realms to sell for instant gold to buy stuff, in this case the items in question.", "creationdate": "2016-08-20T23:33:02-05:00", "id": 962142, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2369755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "wowilovehead", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The phasing was a bug, and was hotfixed out.", "creationdate": "2016-10-27T13:35:20-05:00", "id": 1001823, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2369755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Purgatorywolf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 23, "id": 2369779, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Rrezz", "body": "Easiest method to access this NPC.\r\n\r\n1. Create a level 1 Orc.\r\n\r\n2. Run to the docks.\r\n\r\n3. Buy the toys.\r\n\r\n\r\nI just tested this and my level 1 fresh spawn Orc was able to buy from this NPC. So you do NOT need ot be level 100, you do NOT need any quests or anything at all just the gold to buy the items.\r\n\r\nJust make a level 1 Orc and buy the toys it's as easy as that.\r\n\r\nAs I said I just tested this 5 minutes before this post so it is currently working right now.", "date": "2016-08-17T18:10:45-05:00", "rating": -6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just went with my 71 DK and bought them. Seems like all characters who have not done the pre-event quest yet can access her to buy the toys.", "creationdate": "2016-08-17T18:45:26-05:00", "id": 961321, "rating": -3, "commentid": 2369779, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Stevenseegal", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The phasing was a bug, and was hotfixed out.", "creationdate": "2016-10-27T13:35:03-05:00", "id": 1001822, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2369779, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Purgatorywolf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
