{"commentv2": 1, "number": 27, "id": 2370290, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "taskun56", "body": "Currently there is a glitch that makes anyone see the Broken Isles phase of the docks outside Orgrimmar. That being said, if you can make a level 1 horde toon and mail them a few Renowned Guild Tabards you should be able to buy all of the toys and the shoes. Rav will be on the right side right before the ship. \r\n\r\nGood luck!", "date": "2016-08-18T16:51:54-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It was indeed a glitch, and appears to have been hotfixed out. Heaven forfend that the people who favor Alliance characters get any cool goodies. We get a locket that makes a lady commit suicide instead, then rifle through her possessions and steal her hood.", "creationdate": "2016-08-20T23:53:36-05:00", "id": 962148, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2370290, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Zinovia", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
