{"commentv2": 1, "number": 39, "id": 2450003, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Nothgorb", "body": "for those wanting to get the\"Whole-Body Shrinka'\" but have no horde 100 to get it, just create a trial character,(preferably an orc or troll) hearth as soon as you load in, get the legion quest from the hero's call board in front of you, fly to the location of the quest, do the first quest to get a ring, go to Ravika and sell the ring, you will have enough gold to buy the shrinker and upon activating it, all of your characters will have it as well. I literally just tried this so i know it works.\r\n\r\n-Cheers,\r\nNoth", "date": "2016-12-01T07:01:52-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just to be clear, I also logged onto a different toon to verify that it worked the way I intended and it did, I have access to the toy on another toon on another realm. booyah, problem dealt with in 5 mins or less.", "creationdate": "2016-12-01T07:07:54-06:00", "id": 1013294, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2450003, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Nothgorb", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
