{"commentv2": 1, "number": 42, "id": 2458585, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Saro", "body": "As several comments say, it is true that she can be found at 57, 62 on the Echo Isles, outside of the hut where Vol'jin is.\r\nHowever, on two level 100 chars, I could only see her with the one that had done the artifact quest. For the other char, and for lower level chars, she was simply not there.\r\n\r\nMaybe it's a bug, I don't know - since the alliance version of her, who sells \"Lucky Shirt\" and such, can be seen just fine by all chars.", "date": "2017-01-02T18:12:22-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
