{"commentv2": 1, "number": 44, "id": 2475425, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Malthulhu", "body": "If Ravika does not show up for you like she did not for me as a Demon Hunter you can easily use the 100 Trial Toon to get these items VERY easily. Make your 100 trial, hearth from boat, log out, send gold to that toon, log back in, get the gold, and then fly to where you need to go. \r\nP.S. This is by far the easiest way to obtain all of the racial mounts.", "date": "2017-03-04T02:03:26-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
