{"commentv2": 1, "number": 48, "id": 2511169, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Lilyoptra", "body": "Level 75 couldn't see her in either place. Level 103 Demon Hunter couldn't either. Created trial acccounts and they see her in the Durotar location (did not take the time to check Echo Isles).  If you go the trial account route, make a troll; they get a slight discount.", "date": "2017-07-31T02:08:35-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Make a goblin, they always get the best price.", "creationdate": "2018-04-09T23:15:01-05:00", "id": 1107912, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2511169, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "kathran2119", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 49, "id": 2530192, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "FerrisBuelle", "body": "She's located in the Echo Isles in Durotar, at /way 57.4 62.25\r\nI'm level 110 and have done Broken Isles scenarios, she's accessible to all horde players", "date": "2017-10-17T22:19:47-05:00", "rating": 14, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
