{"commentv2": 1, "number": 51, "id": 2569784, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "PaladinWat", "body": "A few notes: \n[ul]\n[li]\nIt costs approximately 86 gold to buy all four of Ravika's items on a Troll Class Trial character (including the race's Darkspear rep discount). [/li]\n[li] Class Trial characters start with 10 gold and bags & gear that can be vendored.\n[/li]\n\n[li]On a Class Trial character, you can use your regular hearthstone to get directly to Orgrimmar. Once you're there, you can ride out of the city, take a left, and find Ravika near Durotar's eastern shore (/tar ravika).[/li]\n\n[/ul]", "date": "2018-05-25T00:56:08-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thanks. I'd been seriously lagging on leveling my Horde alt, but this was simple as can be to make a trial character, mail them some gold, buy the toys, and delete afterwards.", "creationdate": "2018-07-10T23:48:21-05:00", "id": 1120245, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2569784, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Oneminutemonkey", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-05-26T12:54:56-05:00", 1, "PaladinWat"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 52, "id": 2582622, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Mattly99", "body": "I couldn't find her on my 103 demon hunter in both the docks and Echo Isles. I created a trial character, used the hearthstone, and mailed gold to him. There she was at the docks.", "date": "2018-07-20T02:14:36-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-07-20T02:14:51-05:00", 1, "Mattly99"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 53, "id": 2586393, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Tagara", "body": "[u]As of Patch 8.0.1[/u] you can buy these toys as [b][u]Alliance[/u][/b] on a Boosted 110. Unboosted 110 will not be able to see her.\n\n[npc=113615] is still Hostile and had Level 115 guards near her but with quick reflexes you can [s]suicide [/s]buy them.\n\nUsed my Pre-BFA boosted ALLIANCE Druid with WARMODE OFF to stealth to her and before the level 115 guard could kill me I was able to buy them.\n\nShe is located on [url=http://www.wowhead.com/echo-isles]Echo Isles[/url] at [url=http://www.wowhead.com/maps?data=6453:570620]/way 57, 62\n [/url]\nNo need to do a trial horde account. No need to do Broken shore scenario. Just use the Stormwind portal to Hyjal and fly down.\n\nToys:\n[ol]\n[li][item=97919][/li]\n[li][item=97942][/li]\n[li][item=98552][/li]\n[/ol]\n\nShe also sells Transmog:\n[ol]\n[li][item=97901][/li]\n[/ol]", "date": "2018-07-31T09:49:07-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This did not work for my level 110 alliance character that was never boosted. It also did not work for my level 110 alliance character that was boosted to level 100 and worked up to level 110. This also did not work for my level 110 alliance character that was boosted to level 90 and worked up to level 110. It also did not work for any of my horde characters level 85 and level 14. Maybe it works for an alliance character boosted to level 110.", "creationdate": "2018-07-31T13:33:31-05:00", "id": 1125028, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2586393, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "iIIumnati", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "My druid was boosted to 110 using the BFA boost. I went back with my unboosted 110 warlock and I could NOT see her at Echo Isles.", "creationdate": "2018-08-02T20:37:38-05:00", "id": 1125667, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2586393, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Tagara", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-08-03T23:47:25-05:00", 2, "Tagara"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 54, "id": 2586497, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "iIIumnati", "body": "These are my findings on July 31st, 2018.\r\n\r\nNone of the characters I tried could see Ravika at the dock location in Durotar nor the Darkspear Hold location. These included a level 110 alliance character that was never boosted, a level 110 alliance character that was boosted to level 100 and worked up to level 110, and a level 110 alliance character that was boosted to level 90 and worked up to level 110. It also included a horde character level 85 and level 14. I did not try a level 110 boosted character, and that might work after reading other comments here.\r\n\r\nFinally, I created a Level 100 Troll Shaman \"trial character\" and was able to see Ravika at the Darkspear Hold location and purchase the 3 toys. It started with a \"Shaman trial\" that took about 10 minutes to complete, then led to the Burning Legion Shore campaign scenario which took about 30 minutes to complete. The reward was a staff I sold for about 50 gold which added to the starting gold to give me enough to buy all 3 toys.\r\n\r\nShe is located on Echo Isles at 57, 62 standing on the ground next to a level 115 Darkspear Watcher who is next to the stairs that lead to the entrance of the smallest hut of the three hut complex which is marked on your mini map as a triangular area just above the letter \"D\" in the words \"DARKSPEAR HOLD\".", "date": "2018-07-31T13:56:21-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Confirmed in patch 8.0 I also found her in Echo Isles!", "creationdate": "2018-08-03T15:59:31-05:00", "id": 1125851, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2586497, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Auroraborealiss", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Still works with the trial character, which is now 110. I did the fast training on the airship and logged out when I was on the wyvvern, being asked to accept the scenario. I sent some gold to the trial char, logged in again and stood in front of Orgrimmar. At the Echo Isles I found her right hand side next to the platform opposite to Vol'jins house. get your toys, done. Don't buy the cosmetical feet, the 45 gold would be wasted as they only show your blank feet and not shoes.", "creationdate": "2018-12-07T05:28:59-06:00", "id": 1207975, "rating": -1, "commentid": 2586497, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Inumi", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 55, "id": 2595296, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "wowballerx", "body": "Update for BFA: \r\nWhen I get to her coordinate, she's gone, the surrounding had changed in 8.0. \r\nIs there any way to get to this NPC in BFA?\r\nLike, any way to access and experience the storyline of brokenshore?", "date": "2018-08-16T11:51:27-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "As of October 13, 2018 - She is at her normal coordinates (Echo Isles at /way 57, 62) for my 120 Horde character (boosted).", "creationdate": "2018-10-13T09:14:54-05:00", "id": 1150241, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2595296, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "jbrinley", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 56, "id": 2607829, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "ABloodElfPaladin", "body": "As of 8.0.1 this character is still in the game with the toys and transmog item. I tested it on two characters, both Horde. A mage that played during the SoO patch and a Demon Hunter (who obviously could not have existed during SoO). \r\n\r\nShe was in Darkspear Hold on the Echo Isles for the Mage but *not* for the Demon Hunter, so take that for what you will. :x", "date": "2018-08-31T14:30:02-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "My mage couldn't see her, but my paladin could, odd... Maybe there is some form of phasing going on that requires a certain quest doing to unlock. :O", "creationdate": "2018-09-29T23:50:55-05:00", "id": 1147653, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2607829, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Drayline", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 57, "id": 2614334, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Winning117", "body": "Good news Alliance players, I found a way to get a total of 5 Horde-Only toys using Class Trials in Battle for Azeroth in under 2 hours! This method doesn't require that you make a horde character from level 1 or Boost a character!\n\n[ol]\n[li]Create a Class Trial character (any class except Demon Hunter) and play through the tutorial up until you reach Zandalar. [u]Make sure to not set your Hearthstone anywhere.[/u][/li]\n[li]Complete the quests [quest=46930] and [quest=46931]. If you don\u2019t do these two quests you will be phased and can\u2019t buy from the vendors.[/li]\n[li][code]/way 52.9, 89.9 1. Griftah (buy \"Sack of 'Discarded' Hearthstones\" for 10g)[/code][/li]\n[li][code]/way 34.8, 11.5 2. Rakle the Wretched (get \"Much-Too-Hot Pepper\")[/code][/li]\n[li][code]/way 37.8, 14.7 3. Trader Haw'li (get \"Golden Seeds\")[/code][/li]\n[li][b]Make sure to buy [item=159749] while you\u2019re here[/b][/li]\n[li][code]/way 42.2, 35.7 4. Granda Watae (get \"Centennial Blossom\")[/code][/li]\n[li][code]/way 57.2, 91.5 5. Trader Nog (get \"Preserved Night Elf Head\")[/code][/li]\n[li][code]/way 53.8, 86.0 6. \"Black Eye\" Zenru (get \"Counterfeit Rastakhan Mask\")[/code][/li]\n[li][code]/way 52.9, 89.9 7. Griftah (get \"Zandalari Effigy Amulet\")[/code][/li]\n[li][b]Once you reach Griftah be sure to buy the [item=156649][/b][/li]\n[li]Use hearthstone (will still be set to Orgrimmar)[/li]\n[li][code]/way 57, 62 Echo Isles (Ravika)[/code][/li]\n[li]Buy [item=97919], [item=97942], and [item=98552][/li]\n[li]Learn all of your toys[/li]\n[li]Log into your Alliance characters and enjoy your new toys![/li]\n[/ol]\n\nNow you have 5 more Toys that you can use on your Alliance characters! Cheers!\n\nSpecial thanks to  [url=https://www.wowhead.com/user=Nightswifty]Nightswifty[/url] and [url=https://www.wowhead.com/user=shylee]shylee[/url] for info on how to get the [item=156649].", "date": "2018-09-13T00:58:40-05:00", "rating": 26, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thanks ! +bonus i can see lordaeron scenario form horde side", "creationdate": "2018-11-17T12:56:47-06:00", "id": 1205260, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2614334, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Drdax", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Are these still possible to get by 8.1.5? EDIT: Did it and it worked, got my three toys from Ravika =) Thanks for your post!", "creationdate": "2019-03-28T11:58:11-05:00", "id": 1226295, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2614334, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Soigelasse", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It's worth noting that you need to exit the palace to place the waypoints. I was sure I'd done something wrong and was phased from the npc's.", "creationdate": "2020-02-01T01:22:41-06:00", "id": 1352094, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2614334, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Laschiel", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "can confirm this still works as of today (april 18, 2020)", "creationdate": "2020-04-18T13:35:10-05:00", "id": 1363663, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2614334, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "gulepa", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Still Work on 9.1.0.4 Shadowland September 25, 2021", "creationdate": "2021-09-25T05:35:42-05:00", "id": 1513864, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2614334, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "PunishMent69", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-09-13T01:22:36-05:00", 1, "Winning117"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 58, "id": 2623638, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Kelex", "body": "As of 10/14/2018 I just bought all 4 of them on my 120 Paladin on 8.0 ilvl 344\r\n\r\n[item=97901 domain=www]\r\n[item=97919 domain=www]\r\n[item=97942 domain=www]\r\n[item=98552 domain=www]", "date": "2018-10-14T18:29:54-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "She is here on the island, whilst the island is hostile you can fly to her and she will sell you the toys. I had done all the troll quests and could still see her. Quick way to get there is the boat from Zuldzar.", "creationdate": "2018-10-16T17:17:07-05:00", "id": 1150884, "rating": -1, "commentid": 2623638, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "rzzr", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 59, "id": 2855298, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Hansraj", "body": "I could not see Ravika on my 120 HM Druid. I came back on my Orc Hunter and she's there. My guess is the issue is that I leveled my druid as Alliance and faction changed him at level 110, missing the Horde versions of the Broken Shore questline.", "date": "2018-11-27T20:31:12-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It may require the Broken Shore quest line. That would be consistent with what I found. I went there first on a level 63 belf character, no sign of her. Went back on my 118 orc, and there she was.", "creationdate": "2019-01-09T01:59:10-06:00", "id": 1214612, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2855298, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "dgnuff", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 60, "id": 2868803, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "Sheelac", "body": "[b][u]As of January 29th 2019, this worked for me.[/u]\n[i]Anyone can do it, and it's fast.[/i][/b]\n\n[ol]\n[li]Create a class trial orc or troll (Because Orcs I am sure has their HS set in Orgrimmar, and Trolls might get a slight discount).[/li]\n[li]Login to the world.[/li]\n[li]When on the class trial ship, use your hearthstone. It will send you to Orgrimmar (Don't do the class trial quest, it's not needed).[/li]\n[li]Summon a flying mount and fly to Echo Isles.[/li]\n[li]Go to Ravika, to the right of Vol'jin's hut.[/li]\n[li]Take off all your gear, open boost loot bags, and sell the gear, plus your bags. Nets you about 10g or more.[/li]\n[li]Buy your toys.[/li]\n[/ol]\n\nIf you don't have enough money, log another horde character and send a few, or make another class trial character, sell items and send the gold.\nAnd yes, Ravika is there, atleast if you don't do any quests.\n\n[b]Good luck.[/b]", "date": "2019-01-29T13:43:23-06:00", "rating": 17, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I can confirm this also works for a non-class trial toon (boosted 110, leveled in BoA), without having done any Broken shore quests.", "creationdate": "2019-05-13T19:04:32-05:00", "id": 1301741, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2868803, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "GAFFiO", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "unfortunately, this no longer works. tried it and i couldn't even open the boost bags as a class trial. :\\", "creationdate": "2019-05-17T16:29:03-05:00", "id": 1302100, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2868803, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Zephi5315", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Zephi5315 is right. The class trial bag says \"you cannot do that while on a class trial\" and wont open. The box does tho but its only 45 silver worth. However, I did the steps Sheelac posted with a CT Troll and while on the way to echo isle I stopped off at Zunta pet trainer in Durotar and quickly did the pet battle for 19g40s along with selling my bags and the weapon from the first freebie quest when you hearth in I had more than enough gold to buy all 3 toys, but not the xmog shoes. Had 7g83s50c remaining. Thanks for this tip Sheelac!", "creationdate": "2019-06-11T17:14:30-05:00", "id": 1304912, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2868803, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Belyea", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Awesome. I had 2 Alliance toons that had done the Broken Shore intros. I have one Horde toon @ 120 that had not done the Broken shore intro. None could see this person on Echo Islands. Thus I was very happy that the above strategy worked. 3 new toys with minimal effort. My Horde toon sent 50 gold to the class trial toon. It all worked. Many thanks in 2020 @ 8.3", "creationdate": "2020-05-07T06:22:26-05:00", "id": 1367408, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2868803, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "biggaz13", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I did this just now and it worked great! Thank you!", "creationdate": "2020-07-09T23:47:02-05:00", "id": 1378545, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2868803, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "GraceyViolet", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2019-02-02T16:52:31-06:00", 1, "Sheelac"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 61, "id": 2879899, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "DudeRamRod", "body": "Is anyone else having a hard time finding her with the new 8.2 update? I can not find her by the bloodfist docks or echo isle at all. Nor can my friend with all of our alts.. is this a bug or did they patch her out of the game yet again?", "date": "2019-04-02T04:19:55-05:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "She is on Echo Isle at 57 62", "creationdate": "2019-08-06T22:03:36-05:00", "id": 1321306, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2879899, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Grus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It appears she is only visible on Echo Isles to those characters who have gone through the Legion opening scenario, the initial Broken Shore assault. This becomes available to any level 98 character. She will initially be near the Orgrimmar docks, and after the scenario, she will be in Darkspear Hold on the Echo Isles.", "creationdate": "2020-02-22T20:14:19-06:00", "id": 1355834, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2879899, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Jeromsil", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I didn't see her on my main (troll druid) but logged over to my Zandarali Troll Rogue and she was where she should have been on Echo isles. I don't know why she's there for some but not others. I know that my druid has done the Legion bits, but it might have changed due to the new allied race. Hopefully not, as it would make it pretty much impossible for Alliance to roll and alt and get this stuff, which wouldn't be fair.", "creationdate": "2020-07-21T19:19:32-05:00", "id": 1380425, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2879899, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "sirloper", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "it is patch 9.5,if she is not at the Echo isles place, she is at the Orgimmar docks, when you get to the end, you will see a mammoth, she is nearby in her own hut. the whole body shrinka is such a fun toy, on a gnome LOL!", "creationdate": "2021-04-12T23:39:07-05:00", "id": 1481925, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2879899, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "danicadb1", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
