{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 3266654, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Redroach21", "body": "You should get [spell=339901] and extra action button with the spell [spell=339903] upon killing a High Inquisitor, use it.  [spell=339903] clears [spell=339901].", "date": "2020-12-04T13:13:20-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 3283870, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "jedmao", "body": "I soloed this on my (undergeared) rogue with the following strategy.\n\nThe debuff is called [spell=339900] and it's a quick 1.5s cast, so I used the smaller pillar (kill the 2 trash mobs beside it) so I could run away from it and turn the corner to avoid getting a single stack. As a rogue, this allowed me to let my cooldowns reset so I could stun lock her, deal damage and run away while my energy comes back.\n\nIt seems to me that she casts [spell=339900] immediately after [spell=339905] (which always comes in threes) if it helps you with the timing. You really have to react fast, which is why the smaller pillar is ideal so you can turn a corner faster. [spell=339900] cannot be interrupted, but she can be stun locked.\n\nYou don't have to kill a High Inquisitor to get [spell=339903]. You just have to get 4 stacks of [spell=339901] and the [spell=339903] button will show on your UI. Be careful not to [spell=339903] in the middle of [spell=339905] or you will take significant damage.\n\nBring some potions in case you get [spell=339901] and don't forget those world drop items you can use to deal or prevent significant damage. Now is the time to use all your options.\n\nBTW, if you die after using your sin stone you can keep trying again and again without needing another one. I'm assuming if someone else kills you or swoops in for the kill after you die that you might lose the sin stone. Not sure. Don't get ganked!", "date": "2021-01-01T15:18:00-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2021-01-01T15:26:58-06:00", 10, "jedmao"]}
