{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 3298036, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Mypciscraze", "body": "Hi all\r\n\r\nSmall Guide How to do Exalted Reputation in fast way with [faction=2439] and Achievement [achievement=14276]. Durning Farm reputation in this way You will collect a lot of [currency=1816] ( I get 20k at the end. )\r\n\r\nTo start making reputation You need to first finish Storyline [storyline=1144].\r\n\r\n[u][b]Reputation Guide Video[/b][/u] - https://youtu.be/-GTMOpUSt74\r\n\r\n[storyline=1144] [b]Storyline Video[/b] - https://youtu.be/T5718tr4TgA\r\n\r\n[b]Achievement [achievement=14276] Video[/b] - https://youtu.be/sTxgGWEQffc\r\n\r\n  [b]1.  Befor Start Farm some information:------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[/b]\r\n\r\nAfter Finish Storyline You will be able to Get [item=173793], [item=173794] and [item=173795] From [npc=160248] ( 72 51 inside bulding ) is like finishing Quest. [b]To get new Sinstone from Fane You need to used or remove old one[/b] but you can buy them all the time is no limit.\r\n\r\nYou need Sinstones to Activate Inquisitors. [b]You have 3 type of Inquisitor Sinstones : Green Blue Purple [/b] On Farm We will [b]focus only on Blue and Pruple Sinstones[/b] ( on green is to low reputation ).\r\n\r\n[item=173794] - You need to pay 250 [currency=1816] - [b]Reward[/b] from Killing Inquisitor: [u][b]100 Reputation[/b][/u], 50 [currency=1816], 1 [item=180451] ( 80-85% drop rate )\r\n[item=173795] - You need to pay 10 [item=180451] - [b]Reward[/b] from Killing Inquisitor: [u][b]200 Reputation[/b][/u], 100 [currency=1816]\r\n\r\n[item=173794] is giving one of Sinstones: [item=173000], [item=173001], [item=173005] or [item=173006]\r\n[item=173795] is giving one of Sinstones: [item=173007] or [item=173008]\r\n\r\n[currency=1816] - Is drop from all mobs in this area\r\n[item=180451] - Is drop from Green and Blue Inquisitors\r\n\r\nTo increase reputation You can use 2 thinks:\r\n - Press on Bell 72 49 that will give you buff for 20 min [spell=346713] - to activate you need 30 [currency=1820]\r\n- Drop Guild baner [item=64399].\r\n\r\n[b]2. Set Up Farm and best path:--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[/b]\r\n\r\nFirst Do party/raid or join ( best is raid with 10+ people more people is better ). To start farm All raid mambers are going to [npc=160248] ( 72 51 inside bulding ) And buying [item=173794] and [item=173795] after that You going from Inquisitor to Inquisitor and using all Sinstones then all people are going back to [npc=160248] to get new Sinstones. Is good to use marks next to Inquisitors to prevent using by 2 people Sinstones in same time, call ppl on czat who have Sinstones and ask them to use it one by one. Don't move to next inquisitor until you will not finish all Sinstones respown is small no point to waste time to move back.\r\n\r\nBest Path:\r\n1. Shop ( Buy Sisnstones from [npc=160248] ( 72 51 inside bulding ))\r\n2. [npc=159155] - is over shop 72 53 ( any person who will use his Sinstone on this Inq can go fast shop to get new Sinstone, Shopw is very close )\r\n3. [npc=159154] - Use steps to get to 70 52\r\n4. [npc=159156] - Go west 64.5 52.5\r\n5. [npc=159157] - Go northeast You will need to jump down to 70 45\r\n6. [npc=159153] - Go 71 42\r\n7. [npc=159152] - Go east 75 44 \r\n8. Go Back to Shop Buy Sisnstones from [npc=160248] and start back from Point 2.\r\n\r\nIf You have Raid with over 20+ From Times to Times You can skip Blue Inquisitors and go only Purple [npc=159156] and [npc=159157] due to high number of [item=180451].\r\n\r\n[b]3. Shop - Reward from Reputation:-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[/b]\r\n\r\nAll Items You can buy from [npc=173705] ( 72 51 Revendreth inside bulding ) or [npc=176368] Oribos 46.6 77.6\r\n\r\nList of Items and Requirements:\r\n\r\n- [item=182954] - 2000 [currency=1816], Exalted Reputation and [b]You need to be in Venthyr Covenant[/b]\r\n- [item=184218] - 1000 [currency=1816], Exalted Reputation\r\n- [item=184220] - 1200 [currency=1816], Exalted Reputation\r\n- [item=184221] - 1000 [currency=1816], Exalted Reputation\r\n- [item=182890] - 500 [currency=1816], Revered Reputation\r\n- [item=180940] - 500 [currency=1816], Revered Reputation and [b]You need to be in Venthyr Covenant[/b]\r\n- [item=184219] - 600 [currency=1816], Revered Reputation\r\n- [item=184222] - 350 [currency=1816], Honored Reputation\r\n- [item=182660] - 35 [currency=1816], Honored Reputation\r\n\r\n[b]4. How to do Achievement [achievement=14276] ---------------------------------------------------------[/b]\r\n\r\nBest way to do it is after Reputation Farm ( You should have done Blue and Purple Inquisitors only green will left to do ). You will have a lot of [currency=1816] that will give You chances to reroll [item=173793] to get Sinstons to the missing Inquisitors.\r\n\r\nList of Inquisitors to Slay:\r\n\r\nGreen - [npc=156918] 65 46.5 - To activate You need [item=172998]\r\nGreen - [npc=156919] 67 43 - To activate You need [item=172997]\r\nGreen - [npc=156916] 69.5 47.5 - To activate You need [item=172996] \r\nGreen - [npc=159151] 76 52 - To activate You need [item=172999]\r\nBlue - [npc=159155] 72 53 - To activate You need [item=173006]\r\nBlue - [npc=159152] 75 44 - To activate You need [item=173000]\r\nBlue - [npc=159154] 70 52 - To activate You need [item=173005]\r\nBlue - [npc=159153] 71 42 - To activate You need [item=173001]\r\nPurple - [npc=159157] 70 45 - To activate You need [item=173008]\r\nPurple - [npc=159156] 64.5 52.5 - To activate You need [item=173007]\r\n\r\nHope That Help You :)", "date": "2021-02-05T04:39:58-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
