{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 1719686, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "2Lan", "body": "As of last 5.0.5 patch hotfixes update, the Wharf Rat appears as expected in the Pet Journal.\n\nSource: [url=http://us.battle.net/wow/en/blog/7207170/Patch_505_Hotfixes_-9_25_2012]Wow 5.0.5 hotfixes 9.25.2012 official site[/url]", "date": "2012-09-26T05:25:23-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He does now appear on the list, however does not count toward Eastern Kingdom's Safari. I kept catching them and eventually got a rare, but they still aren't checked off for the achievement.", "creationdate": "2012-10-02T10:26:33-05:00", "id": 577836, "rating": 5, "commentid": 1719686, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "265695", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "@RTalons I contacted a GM about this, it also happens sometimes to 'bought' pets like the dragonhawks. This is a known bug.", "creationdate": "2012-10-06T01:37:50-05:00", "id": 579995, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1719686, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Wolfwings", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I have the same problem, caught 2 now and it's not checked off.", "creationdate": "2012-11-25T22:44:24-06:00", "id": 603078, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1719686, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "illiterate", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Will get checked off if you catch it in the listed zone of capture(beeing the cape of Booty Bay and not the city/harbor of Booty Bay).", "creationdate": "2013-05-06T20:29:14-05:00", "id": 656793, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1719686, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "