{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 402831, "nreplies": 8, "sticky": 0, "user": "Starfox", "body": "After i got http://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44502 i was able to buy mats from her\r\nhttp://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44501 1000g (need 8 per mount)\r\nhttp://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44500 1500g _LIMITED SUPPLY_\r\nhttp://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44499 3000g\r\n12500gold per mount for those mats alone", "date": "2008-10-11T12:07:08-05:00", "rating": 51, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Well you won't see many hogs on the AH for a very long time.", "creationdate": "2008-10-15T12:42:22-05:00", "id": 354709, "rating": 2, "commentid": 402831, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Tsuwulf", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Auction house also takes a certain cut, so putting something up for 13k gold will net you less than 12.5k, so it'll have to put up for a really high price. Think that's what he ment", "creationdate": "2008-11-15T05:47:14-06:00", "id": 360698, "rating": 9, "commentid": 402831, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "41851", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The deposit is based on the 5g vendor amount.  That is only a cost if the auction does not sell, as it is added to your proceeds if the item sells.  The AH takes a 5% commission based on the Selling Price, which will exceed 12.5k, since that is the cost of the mats alone.  The neutral AH takes 15% by the way.  So, don't look for these on the AH.  Ever.  Now, I see \"Limited Edition\".  Can someone confirm that they are, in fact, in limited supply, how many that supply is, and how often it is \"restocked\" ?", "creationdate": "2008-11-17T16:58:09-06:00", "id": 56944, "rating": 14, "commentid": 402831, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, 