{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 454985, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Junyed", "body": "Possibly a reference to Roxy Rocket, a character created for the DC animated universes Batman comic series, put into the show years later, and eventually the regular DC universe itself.", "date": "2008-11-19T03:13:07-06:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I personally thought of Rikki Rockett from the glam metal band Poison from the 80's.  They did often dress like girls for their preformances :-P  http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rikki_Rockett", "creationdate": "2008-12-21T19:54:32-06:00", "id": 66700, "rating": 9, "commentid": 454985, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Royi", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "or, seeing how she's a riding/[b]flying[/b] trainer it could also be a reference to [url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_Ramjet]Roger Ramjet[/url], the 1965 cartoon fighter pilot  seeing how wow doesn't contain any jetfighters, but it does have rockets: ram-jet becomes ram-rocket", "creationdate": "2009-11-30T10:12:23-06:00", "id": 134769, "rating": 9, "commentid": 454985, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Stripfiguur", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 467644, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Eliasar", "body": "Also teaches [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=34091]Artisan[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=34090]Expert[/url] Riding.", "date": "2008-11-24T17:34:52-06:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Do NOT learn [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=34090]Expert Riding[/url] or [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=34091]Artisan Riding[/url] from her. You can learn these cheaper with rep discounts. Alliance can learn from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=35100]Hargen Bronzewing[/url] (Stormwind rep discount) or [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=35133]Maigra Keenfeather[/url] (Valiance Expedition rep discount). Horde can learn from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=35093]Wind Rider Jahubo[/url] (Orgrimmar rep discount) or [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=35135]Wind Rider Sabamba[/url] (Warsong Offensive", "creationdate": "2008-11-24T17:34:53-06:00", "id": 448233, "rating": 21, "commentid": 467644, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "corilan75", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Is it true that an engineer can buy only 1of Elementium-plated Exhaust Pipe  and never can buy 1 more? I heard this rumor on some chat,  just want to see if it\u2019s true", "creationdate": "2008-12-02T07:23:22-06:00", "id": 366115, "rating": 1, "commentid": 467644, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "41137", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "No you can buy as many as you want, it's just on a respawn timer.", "creationdate": "2008-12-03T03:47:10-06:00", "id": 366506, "rating": 7, "commentid": 467644, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Sonaria", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "However, because she has no faction, you're almost certainly better off learning them from someone else.", "creationdate": "2009-09-19T22:05:54-05:00", "id": 122903, "rating": 25, "commentid": 467644, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "bombcar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
