{"commentv2": 1, "number": 13, "id": 656447, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Doeg", "body": "Actually, if you're not already 450 Engineering there is no hurry. Just buy the mats for a couple of Heartseeker Scopes and sell the crafted scope on the AH (don't flood the AH though), where you should be able to make some, or all, of your costs back. Rinse and repeat. Make goggles for the 450 point. No need for gold buying to reach 450.\r\n\r\nAnd 12500g is a lot, but no worse a grind than epic flight was in TBC.", "date": "2009-03-26T14:11:52-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 14, "id": 731842, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "349853", "body": "it took me alot of dailys but i finaly got all the mats\r\ni could not get them untill i got http://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44502\r\nthen what i did was when people wanted me 2 make them the mount i told them i could buy them the mats but for an extra 50g \r\nhttp://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44501 1000g each they need 8 so i earn 400g\r\nhttp://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44500 1500g each ( limited stock ) so i charge 100g \r\nhttp://wotlk.wowhead.com/?item=44499 3000g each i earn 50g\r\nso after doing all that i earn 550g\r\nthen i make it and charge them 200g tip \r\nso all in all i make 750g ( not bad ) :)", "date": "2009-05-30T04:59:39-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "you made 750g cool - how much did the materials you didnt list cost?   Assuming i read the correct information and AH takes 5% if it cost you 12.5k to make (not considering the additional mats missing in the above post), the minimum you would sell it to recover your expense is 13.2k (13,200 less 5% >660g< will net 12,540 gold)   If you sold it at 15K = 15k less 5% (750g) = 14250g less 12.5k= [b][u]1750g[/u][/b]    If you sold it for 20k = 20k less 5% (1k) = 19000g less 12.5k = [b][u]6500g[/u][/b]  If you're wondering how much profit you will make if you buy the other mats (titansteel barx12, c", "creationdate": "2009-05-30T04:59:40-05:00", "id": 442969, "rating": 1, "commentid": 731842, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "329944", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "you did not get a tip. you charged them to make it, a tip is something the customer gives depending on whether or not they were given quality service.", "creationdate": "2009-07-18T19:40:25-05:00", "id": 110503, "rating": 18, "commentid": 731842, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "kinark", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-05-30T05:03:29-05:00", 1, "349853"]}
