{"commentv2": 1, "number": 26, "id": 1305065, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Greken", "body": "i went there to get my chopper parts this night and ill noticed what everyone have been saying she IS NOT selling any parts whats so ever and this is freaking retarded tbh.\r\n\r\nill hope thay fix this soon cuz we need to get to tha choppa", "date": "2011-01-22T23:45:54-06:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Someone noted above that you need to already know one of the two schematics for her shopping interface to show up. Did you already buy and learn one of the schematics? I just now bought parts from her myself.", "creationdate": "2011-01-27T11:35:05-06:00", "id": 219358, "rating": 4, "commentid": 1305065, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "12727", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Are you a goblin? I am and I talked to a GM today after having the same issue and I was told that Goblins currently cannot learn the schematic and if you knew it before you became a goblin then you no longer do and are unable to relearn it. The Worgen have the same issue on alliance side from what he told me.  And he provided no ETA on when it'll be fixed either >.>", "creationdate": "2011-01-29T16:15:21-06:00", "id": 220015, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1305065, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "UnlimitedAnza", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I went to the the alliance vanguard quartermaster and bought the recipe for the Mekgineer's Chopper on my worgen rogue, no trouble what so ever buying/learning it. Also no trouble buying the parts from this npc.", "creationdate": "2011-04-22T08:23:33-05:00", "id": 239047, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1305065, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "H