{"commentv2": 1, "number": 31, "id": 1435030, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "skantasm", "body": "While the Goblin race first received the full 20% discount from this vendor, this is no longer the case. I actually submitted a ticket and received this GM response:\r\n\r\n[code][GM] We forewarded this to our Quality Assurance people and they determined that it's not a bug.  This vendor NPC has no associated faction, the discount for Goblins treats them as if they were exalted with all factions.\r\n[GM] It's the same deal with Michelle De Rum.  Other notable vendors who have no faction affiliation are Yasmin, Helpful Jungle Money, and Salvaged Goods.\r\n[GM] It's possible the vendor had a faction affilation at one point, that is no longer the case.[/code]\r\n\r\nIf this vendor never had a faction affiliation before, then the 20% discount was likely a bug.", "date": "2011-06-05T17:05:45-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 32, "id": 1435708, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Otium", "body": "As a Dranei Engineer I DID get a discount, asif friendly / honored / revered / exalted, although it doesn't state which faction she belongs to.\r\nHer name's in green, and for me the prices are:\r\nPiston 900\r\nSalvaged parts 2700\r\nExhaust pipe 1350\r\nThat's 1250 or 10% off\r\n\r\nAm Ambassador, but K3's are still yellow / neutral\r\nso really don't know why the discount", "date": "2011-06-06T14:44:25-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "10% guild discount, I would bet.", "creationdate": "2011-07-07T00:06:15-05:00", "id": 250664, "rating": 9, "commentid": 1435708, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "LuckyGhoul", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
