{"commentv2": 1, "number": 39, "id": 1656168, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "980824", "body": "in found her but i can't buy anything\r\n\r\nsomeone pls help me", "date": "2012-04-19T15:11:21-05:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 16384, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Back in WotLK, you need to be an [b]Enginner[/b] and you must learn the schematic first ([item=44502]/[item=44503]), otherwise she don't sell the itens. I don't know if anything of this changed, because I'm already have the recipe.", "creationdate": "2012-04-19T15:20:17-05:00", "id": 537138, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1656168, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "rsabin", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 40, "id": 1717598, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "lahtinen", "body": "Guys just to clarify as people seem to be still having issues with making purchases:\r\n[ul]\r\n[li]She will only sell you the items if you are an engineer (and probably need to be high enough level to see them, I havent tested this as I am Cata-maxed, maybe someone can look into this?)[/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[ul]\r\n[li]The prices that Wowhead display are the normal, non-reduced prices that you would pay with no discounts at all (eg. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=83964/bartering]bartering[/url] ) so what youre seeing isn't modified by your personal discounts, as is the case with ALL prices on Wowhead, except where noted.[/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[ul]\r\n[li]Finally, she is not located inside K3, but, is actually near the flight master, hence her flying trainer tag under her name.[/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n\r\nAll the best folks! :)", "date": "2012-09-23T13:36:39-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It would seem that you need to be of a certain engineering level in order to buy from her. I just visited her on my engineer, as of writing he's level 71 and has 355 engineering, and she did not have a purchase option available, merely flying lessons. -- [b]Update 1:[/b] Still no purchase option at level 73 with 425 Engineering.", "creationdate": "2012-10-31T12:17:57-05:00", "id": 593449, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1717598, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "466885", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "There seems to be a minimum level requirement too then. 450 Engineering on a level 70 with no option to purchase.", "creationdate": "2012-12-09T12:28:23-06:00", "id": 609740, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1717598, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ogkspaz", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "According to Wowwiki, you also have to have learned the recipe for the Mekgineer's Chopper/Mechano-hog in order to see the items. I can't yet verify this as I don't have the recipe yet, but I am maxed out engineering and she only sells flying training for me.", "creationdate": "2014-11-06T20:12:09-06:00", "id": 786733, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1717598, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "FrostWolf219", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
