{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2569482, "nreplies": 18, "sticky": 0, "user": "varenne", "body": "[npc=135939] rare is located in [zone=9042] [b]The Amber Waves[/b] on Kul Tiras isle.\nIt's in the underground cave near the [b]Amber Waves[/b] village west from [b]Brennadam[/b].\nYou can enter the cave from the hole near the shed, [b]it's north of the Alliance flight master[/b]. \nIt is shaded by a few trees and a small hill, you can see two broken carriages nearby.\nDrops [item=158299].\n\nFor TomTom users\n[b]/way Stormsong Valley 49.65 70.05 Vinespeaker Ratha[/b]\n[B]/way Stormsong Valley 50.89 69.81 Cave Entrance[/B]\n\n[quote][npc=135939] location video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YufqBHbUaSs[/quote]\nStormsong Valley rares achievement: [achievement=12940]", "date": "2018-05-22T18:32:45-05:00", "rating": 433, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I dont understand this because the cave entrance coodinates are by the flight master. Like exactly in front of him..", "creationdate": "2018-08-18T11:46:20-05:00", "id": 1131540, "rating": 14, "commentid": 2569482, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Cinderhella", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "There are actually two entrances into the cave where [npc=135939] spawns. One at 51, 68 and the other at 51, 67.", "creationdate": "2018-08-18T15:21:13-05:00", "id": 1131647, "rating": 31, "commentid": 2569482, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Griff", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The actual entrance is at 51, 68.7. Just north of the flight master, between a broken wagon cart and the building that kind of looks like a stable.", "creationdate": "2018-08-18T21:19:56-05:00", "id": 1131834, "rating": 91, "commentid": 2569482, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Nukken", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Thank you Nukken. Your tips was perfect for me!", "creationdate": "2018-09-07T03:27:50-05:00", "id": 1141293, "rating": 6, "commentid": 2569482, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Locktose", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "oh there. did not see the giant hole. would have been much easier if i knew which way was north. my sense of direction wins the day again. i kept going around the back of that ally area instead of in front of it.", "creationdate": "2018-11-03T11:16:52-05:00", "id": 1191693, "rating": 5, "commentid": 2569482, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "deacontaylor", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-08-21T17:08:35-05:00", 4, "varenne"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2578163, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Boxofbeer", "body": "[npc=135939] rare mob can be found in [zone=9042].\r\n[ul]\r\n[li][b]Location[/b]: 49.8 70.0[/li]\r\n[li][b]Part of[/b]: [achievement=12940][/li]\r\n[li][b]World Quest:[/b] [quest=52301][/li]\r\n[li][b]Rare drop:[/b] [item=158299 bonus=0][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\nTravel to the Amber Waves flight master and move straight to the north.\r\nThere will be a passage down to the cave, where the rare is.\r\n[quote]TomTom:\r\n/way Stormsong Valley 51.0 68.6  Vinespeaker Ratha[/quote]\r\n\r\n[npc=135939] - www.youtube.com/watch?v=mOV_cWYoJU4", "date": "2018-07-03T11:13:40-05:00", "rating": 28, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The hole is about 20 feet north of the flight master, don't look all around the area like I did, it is very close.", "creationdate": "2018-07-19T05:08:12-05:00", "id": 1121800, "rating": 17, "commentid": 2578163, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DDavis8704", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Cave entrance is 51.63, 67.67 exactly, don't listen to people who tell you to go north of the FP or near a cart, it's on the side of the furthest north building near the FP.", "creationdate": "2019-02-16T00:37:57-06:00", "id": 1220062, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2578163, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "GreySage", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
