{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 2617320, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "sno4270", "body": "To find the original cave entrance, look on your map for the 3 part, upside down shaped Y intersection left of the word Brennadam. I was tripped up on a dif post by assuming the T in the road was referencing the intersection halfway between Brennadam & Deadwash. That's way too far away.\n\nStand on the rock (optional) next to the broken cart w/ corn ears on the ground and wheat icon stamped bags in the cart at the aforementioned intersection. Place yourself so that one of the fields w/ Orc Raiders patrolling is to your right, and the Mechanical farmhands field is to your left, with your back in line w/ the road dividing these 2 fields. You should see a building straight ahead of you with Faithful Watchdogs in the area around the building. Start heading towards that building straight on. You might not have noticed from the intersection based on how your camera was panned, but as you get closer to the building you should see an entrance to a cave, and if you placed yourself appropriately will be set up to head into it. Continue straight into the smaller cave entrance you see once are in the bigger cave entrance. Ta da!\n\nI know this may be more wordy, but without knowing offhand where Farmer Burton and the Alliance flightpath were as I'm horde, and already being deep into Burton's Farmstead when I saw the star for this rare, this was a PIA to follow other directions. The reference to The Amber Waves * almost * helped, except I couldn't remember where I'd gone through that zone.\n\nAlso, if you are deep in Burton's Farmstead and basically on top of the star but not seeing a cave, you need to head back to the road to higher ground and follow the directions above. When you are in the lower part next to rocky hill side wondering where the heck this cave is people are speaking of, if you could scale that hillside you would be at the watchdog building where the cave entrances are.", "date": "2018-09-21T04:21:23-05:00", "rating": 61, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "You're a genius! Co-ords at the entrance to the cave are 51.62, 67.67", "creationdate": "2018-10-08T01:41:37-05:00", "id": 1149335, "rating": 20, "commentid": 2617320, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Lyariana", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "GreySage, I dunno what you did wrong but this worked perfectly for me (and at least 19 other people apparently).", "creationdate": "2018-10-23T01:53:02-05:00", "id": 1152140, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2617320, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "voodoopimp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I'm not sure what you are talking about in regards to either my post or the video you reference. I hope you're not getting confused somehow with nearby WQ Ragna (that's the only thing I can think of to explain the confusion) or another Vinespeaker in the area?", "creationdate": "2018-10-28T03:35:36-05:00", "id": 1153070, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2617320, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "sno4270", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I could not find the way with this comment, sorry... The cave actually has two entrances - one at 51.62, 67.67 as Lyariana wrote, but also at 51.08, 68.71", "creationdate": "2019-01-02T13:33:51-06:00", "id": 1213384, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2617320, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Adelajn", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Genius! much thanks", "creationdate": "2020-07-15T00:28:32-05:00", "id": 1379302, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2617320, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "PicklesForever", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-09-23T20:18:24-05:00", 1, "sno4270"]}
