{"commentv2": 1, "number": 8, "id": 2871637, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "CornDog", "body": "To find Vinespeaker Ratha:\r\n\r\n1. Fly to the Amber Waves flight path.\r\n2. Mount up and ride North-Northeast for about 3 seconds until you are standing at 3 large mechanical farmhand golems.\r\n3. Just look around and you will see a hole in the ground right there. There is a large burning torch and a wrecked cart.\r\n4. Go in the hole and kill Ratha.", "date": "2019-02-15T19:36:20-06:00", "rating": 14, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
