{"commentv2": 1, "number": 13, "id": 3146252, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Wowzir", "body": "[u][b][quest=52301] Quest[/b][/u]\n\n[i]Just for reference, the Flight Point OP have mentioned is the Amber Waves FP.[/i]\n\nFirst step is OPTIONAL for those with flying:\n[b]/way Stormsong Valley 51.0, 68.1 Land on center of roof[/b]\n\nFor the next step, it is easiest to be facing toward the NORTH when you \n[b]/way Stormsong Valley 51.0, 68.7 Descend into hole[/b]\n\nYes, very astute! You noticed the HOLE is due SOUTH of the roof landing.\n\nNow, simply go down the winding tunnel to [npc=135939]\n[b]/way Stormsong Valley 49.8, 68.2 Vinespeaker Ratha[/b]\n\n\n*****************************************************************************\n[i]Clear copy of waypoints only for cut & paste:[/i]\n\n/way Stormsong Valley 51.0, 68.1 Land on center of roof\n/way Stormsong Valley 51.0, 68.7 Descend into hole\n/way Stormsong Valley 49.8, 68.2 Vinespeaker Ratha\n\n*****************************************************************************\n\n;)", "date": "2019-08-09T02:23:52-05:00", "rating": 36, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "life saver thanks so much", "creationdate": "2019-11-27T17:32:49-06:00", "id": 1341299, "rating": 3, "commentid": 3146252, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "xWoWAholicx", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2019-08-09T02:24:35-05:00", 1, "Wowzir"]}
