{"commentv2": 1, "number": 15, "id": 3216740, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Accuda", "body": "Very hard to find, the location is a cave inside the cave.  what makes it harder there is a different cave system , that will take to 2 other named mobs, but is not connected to  this NPCs cave.    coming from the south  look for a broken wagon at 50.99,68.75    go into that cave then follow it to  the NPC's  cave entrance at 50.76,68.17  she dies spawns and dies quick,  so finding her is the hard part.", "date": "2020-07-10T09:08:56-05:00", "rating": 27, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thank you for the broken wagon tip. There are actually two splits in the ground on different sides of the building near the broken wagon. I found the second one on my way out after finishing the quest.", "creationdate": "2020-09-06T07:34:13-05:00", "id": 1388341, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3216740, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "arthas28zp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "CAVE? It's a BURROW, not a cave. It goeas down immediately.", "creationdate": "2021-02-27T00:52:46-06:00", "id": 1454728, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3216740, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "WokkaD", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "If you're Horde, you will probably get flagged for PvP and one shot by guards when you try to enter this cave. I was, however, able to find him while in ghost form and rez near him.", "creationdate": "2021-09-05T19:20:46-05:00", "id": 1510988, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3216740, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "eKatherine", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledE