{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 432853, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "240859", "body": "I just got one question, can u kill him in phase one or what happens if u try that?", "date": "2008-11-06T05:57:55-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He esplodes, you die all :-/", "creationdate": "2008-12-01T18:49:18-06:00", "id": 365945, "rating": 1, "commentid": 432853, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ikir", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "when you kill him in fase 1 as in not all the eggs gone your stuck. they won't respawn. so Lvl 80 going for achievement look out  or we just had a bugged run", "creationdate": "2008-12-28T15:28:37-06:00", "id": 375389, "rating": 0, "commentid": 432853, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "sirmarkus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 11, "id": 538214, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Ant1dote", "body": "Ok, i just had a Sinister Strike crit of 10K on him. on level 80... how come? im not seeing anything about him getting more damage recieved?", "date": "2008-12-30T16:07:11-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 12, "id": 596920, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "288645", "body": "Razorgore is impossible to solo as once you kill him in phase 1 you are instantly killed by an AoE.\r\n\r\nRequires a minimum of 2 people", "date": "2009-02-05T17:10:41-06:00", "rating": 46, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 1, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "If your attempting to 2 man this I would highly advise that whoever is killing the adds stands on the opposite side of the room, the adds will run to the controller however they will drop aggro as soon as they get to him/her.  If you tank them next to the controller you risk being cleaved or getting hit by a Arcane Explosion. The same goes if you attempt to tank them near the platform that the orb is on due to the fact that instead of the casters having to run across the room to you, as soon as they swap aggro from the controller they will just stand next to him/her casting Shadow Bolts and oc", "creationdate": "2009-02-05T17:10:42-06:00", "id": 483325, "rating": 2, "commentid": 596920, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "648653", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Thought it would be a great idea to solo farm BWL on my prot pally, then got one shotted by the first boss. Blow to morale.", "creationdate": "2010-09-11T15:25:01-05:00", "id": 181531, "rating": 19, "commentid": 596920, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "543855", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Razorgore is/was not that hard to do 2man tbh. Me and a friend have been doing it since cata came. He's a prot war running around with the mobs and keeping them away from me(the controller).  But now after the latest patch we can't kill him. After the eggs are destroyed he blows up for no reason other than \"the orb is loosing it's power\" blabla.", "creationdate": "2011-02-24T13:03:51-06:00", "id": 227941, "rating": 1, "commentid": 596920, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "steken", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You have to keep him in combat once the MC breaks and the controller can get control again (at 60, this was no problem, but at 85, we just kill things too fast).  Sometimes this takes a little bit, or bugs.  After several wipes, we had a pally tank him when MC broke, and until the controller could get MC back.", "creationdate": "2011-03-12T10:35:17-06:00", "id": 231729, "rating": 2, "commentid": 596920, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kyokun", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "If you have a paladin, just put on RF and heal yourself. That will pull all the enemies to you, leaving your partner on the orb without getting hit. Basically I spam divine storm at the boss and follow him around as he kills the eggs, and heals myself and kills the monsters with divine storm.", "creationdate": "2012-05-05T02:43:30-05:00", "id": 541212, "rating": 1, "commentid": 596920, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "milo210", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 13, "id": 600329, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "MMOSimca", "body": "Tips for doing BWL with few very people:\r\n\r\nRazorgore - Have the tank grab all the adds and tank in the middle of the room. Have the healer stand on top of the tank and pull healing aggro to get the mobs to the tank. Have a dps kill the blackwing mages ONLY (if you only have 3 people, ignore this role). You could probably 2-man this with a Blood DK tanking the mobs and one player on the orb.", "date": "2009-02-08T10:55:52-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 14, "id": 612992, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "205601", "body": "I did 2man (warrior and dk) razorgore, Warrior tanked mobs and DK handle mindcontrol", "date": "2009-02-17T11:30:43-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Warrior healed himself with bloodthirst (+bloodthirst glyph), Enraged regeneration and Blood DK used runetap (with glyph it heals party members) before he tooked new mindcontrol. I used spec http://www.wowhead.com/?talent=LMZhE00xVzbLoZVIxrx00i0I. And nexttime when ill kill him ill fraps it.", "creationdate": "2009-02-23T07:37:55-06:00", "id": 81952, "rating": 7, "commentid": 612992, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "205601", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 15, "id": 620931, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Suzaru", "body": "Did a 2 man (Heal Shaman, Fire Mage) today, too!\r\nThe Shaman kited the whole adds and i managed the mind control thing...\r\nRazorgore was easy going, mage with decent gear can tank him :D", "date": "2009-02-23T18:18:42-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-02-23T18:18:59-06:00", 1, "Suzaru"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 16, "id": 699982, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "258919", "body": "Allow me to give you a tip, if you're running with a small group of 80s.\r\n\r\nDO NOT START UNTIL EVERY DPS IN THE GROUP KNOWS HOW TO CONTROL THE BOSS.\r\n\r\nI was the controller and got most of the eggs down, but my toon was damaged so I lost the control and still had the debuff. I told our hunter to use the orb, and he did, but he didn't smash the remaining eggs and just stood there. So the mobs killed him and we all died.\r\n\r\n\r\nChances are, you will have to switch off control at least once. Make sure every dpser knows what to do.\r\n\r\nAlso, when your channeling bar is about to die, bring the boss as far away from the orb platform as you can so you won't get attacked by him. Especially if you're a clothie.", "date": "2009-04-30T14:40:03-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-04-30T14:58:17-05:00", 1, "258919"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 17, "id": 719561, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "295146", "body": "2-manned today. =]\n\nProt paladin and ret paladin.\n\nRet pally controls Razorgore.\n\nProt pally just kept laying down consecrates on the stairs for incoming aggro while picking everything else up with ranged and melee attacks, using every free moment to run over and grab everything off the boss and come right back.\n\nGood luck.", "date": "2009-05-18T02:08:33-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I am guessing this has been changed in recent patches. You get a debuff that makes it impossible to mind control him for a time. We just recently tried to 2 man this fight so that my hunter could get to the second to last boss and tame him for a pet.   The fight started off just fine. I took first mind control and when i was kicked off, my friend took the second... When he was kicked off, i tried to regain mind control and was unable to do so, with such a cool down that the adds were able to kill the boss and in so detonating the massive aoe.", "creationdate": "2010-12-06T19:46:51-06:00", "id": 199906, "rating": 1, "commentid": 719561, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "518054", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-05-18T02:47:07-05:00", 7, "295146"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 18, "id": 734218, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "82529", "body": "if you kill him before all the dragon eggs are destroyed he will do a heavy explosion kiling everyone regardless of health, though it can be avoided using divine shield, ice block etc (haven't tried anti-magic shell)", "date": "2009-06-01T12:55:04-05:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "So if I was to solo him in phase 1 and bubble before he dies would it count as a kill? Or at least let me go further?", "creationdate": "2009-09-24T05:02:49-05:00", "id": 425897, "rating": 0, "commentid": 734218, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "36907", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "OK, that explains why when myself in Fury mode and a Hunter easily 2-manned Razorgore (I was doing absurd damage to him, about 3 times my normal crits) easily downed him before pretty much any adds spawned and then bam the explosion and we died. The enconter reset then even though Razorgore was downed.", "creationdate": "2010-01-22T00:59:51-06:00", "id": 439427, "rating": 0, "commentid": 734218, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Superczar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Nope it won't do a jack %^&*, I tried and got blown to bit", "creationdate": "2011-02-11T17:20:29-06:00", "id": 224120, "rating": 0, "commentid": 734218, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DTJames", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 19, "id": 738269, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Rizz", "body": "2 manned by a frost dps DK, and a holy paladin. Needless to say pally was the one who tanked all adds while I (DK) was MC'ing the boss and destroying eggs.", "date": "2009-06-05T18:13:55-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 790192, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Funga", "body": "Hey, I was trying to 2 man it via 3.2 PTR and had a problem. I found that me (80 druid) and my friend (80 Pally) could do it fine up until Razorgore first broke free. He then, before I could hit the orb again, Would suicidally explode and kill us both. Anyone have any Idea whats going on?", "date": "2009-07-27T12:34:25-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 1, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Confirmed on 3.2 PTR that MC'ing him more than once blew him up and wiped us, and there were not even any adds attacking him. Grethok and his adds were killed, we did everything we were supposed to in the fight, (keeping the adds off Razorgore and the person assigned to MC as well) and yet every time the orb was clicked again, Razorgore did his Arcane Explosion that wipes the raid which he only casts when he dies before the eggs are destroyed and reset the encounter. There were absolutely no mobs on him, so he didn't do it because he died, since he hadn't died (I targeted him on other attempts", "creationdate": "2009-07-27T12:34:26-05:00", "id": 417675, "rating": 5, "commentid": 790192, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "wowelderscrolls", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Blizz noted as bug - being fixed on live servers on 08/05/2009 per [url=http://forums.worldofwarcraft.com/thread.html?topicId=19110152523&sid=1]this[/url] blue post.", "creationdate": "2009-08-06T07:26:29-05:00", "id": 114112, "rating": 6, "commentid": 790192, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Konstantinus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
