{"commentv2": 1, "number": 75, "id": 1540057, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Smalblu", "body": "This boss has an affinity for exploding, it seems, as due to the evade bug, he blew up my 10-man guild ach hunting group [b]26[u][/u][/b] times (yes, i counted,) before we called it.", "date": "2011-10-11T00:25:24-05:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "...you gotta do the boss the correct way...there's no way to blast through it =/", "creationdate": "2012-04-17T06:45:04-05:00", "id": 536603, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1540057, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "karatechop", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
