{"commentv2": 1, "number": 313, "id": 2344784, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "Breezie001", "body": "This is the easiest way I found to solo Razorgore.\r\n\r\n[ol]\r\n[li]Stand at the bottom of the platform of the orb. [i]Not sure if this is important but it makes it easier to agro adds[/i].[/li]\r\n[li]Click the orb from the bottom of the platform to control Razorgore.[/li]\r\n[li]While controlling Razorgore click '4' to destroy all the eggs.[/li]\r\n[/ol]\r\n\r\n[b]IMPORTANT: The key is to position your camera to see the orb at all times. You can click the orb as Razorgore from anywhere in the room. When you get a few adds or your channel is low click the orb. You should lose all agro on Razoregore. [/b]", "date": "2016-06-25T13:36:01-05:00", "rating": 33, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "+1 Absolutely brilliant. Was failing for an hour, tried this, confirmed 100 percent.", "creationdate": "2016-07-03T01:03:45-05:00", "id": 949851, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2344784, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Necromanic", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "thank you very much", "creationdate": "2016-07-05T12:40:36-05:00", "id": 950243, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2344784, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Huntercraft192", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You are genius! This worked perfectly the first time. Raz didn't lose less than 75% health. Thank you very much!", "creationdate": "2016-07-22T09:16:54-05:00", "id": 953469, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2344784, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Cailan", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I can NOT upvote this enough! Works as of 7.0.3! He didn't even get below 90%. Thank you so much! <3", "creationdate": "2016-07-28T06:03:26-05:00", "id": 955237, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2344784, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "hjp426", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Works like a charm. Be sure to turn off nameplates so they wont overlap and cover Orb wich makes harder for clicking it.", "creationdate": "2016-08-02T00:03:33-05:00", "id": 956492, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2344784, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kyok", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 314, "id": 2345781, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "limpa71", "body": "You can use the orb from anywhere in the room, so just use that to aggro the mobs from razorgore", "date": "2016-06-28T12:47:14-05:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "no, that isnt true...", "creationdate": "2016-09-09T17:58:20-05:00", "id": 973430, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2345781, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "mro1337", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
