{"commentv2": 1, "number": 363, "id": 2554225, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Guldoran", "body": "So they took the time to make the boss go faster but they haven't taken the time to fix the boss bugging out if you kill it before the eggs are done? This is ridiculous! THEY KNOW this is a bug. This has been a bug for I don't know how long! You mean to tell me they can't put a fix on this boss to PROPERLY reset if the encounter wipes you? Give me a break.", "date": "2018-02-21T14:45:27-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "You misspelled \"Mechanic\". Don't touch the boss at all until the eggs are gone and nothing bad can happen.", "creationdate": "2018-06-19T20:23:39-05:00", "id": 1117098, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2554225, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "sniperorc", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
