{"commentv2": 1, "number": 365, "id": 2556253, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "GazaC76", "body": "Ok here are too many walk throughs on here that take forever to explain. \n\nLET'S SIMPLIFY THIS\n\n1, Kill the controller\n2, click the orb and take Possession Razorgore\n3, Start at the back of the room and use your kill egg ability working your way to the front of the room (you can keep running non stop as ability now insta-cast instead of 3 sec timer).\n4, Kill Razorgore\n5, Get LOOT\n\nYou don't need to leave boss and nuke adds and reposses, it is easy enough to just run your little ass off, nuke eggs, nuke boss and collect LOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOTZ for X-MOGG\n\nDisclaimer: Eggs were fried in a safe manner and wearing full PPE during the making of this comment\n\nWarning: If you are a member of Green Peace, then you will not like the inhumane way that eggs are fried and Dragons are killed in this Zone. Enter at your own risk", "date": "2018-03-05T04:34:05-06:00", "rating": 79, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Perfect! This worked flawlessly for me today!", "creationdate": "2018-09-16T14:41:48-05:00", "id": 1144216, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2556253, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "MacraeCC", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Working as of 8.3. Thank you!", "creationdate": "2020-04-13T13:00:49-05:00", "id": 1362771, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2556253, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "NiceGentleman", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Still works! Thank you!", "creationdate": "2021-05-22T04:05:40-05:00", "id": 1489238, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2556253, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "bomigabster", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Um....Ok...THIS. Delete every other idea. Just....THIS. Thank you.", "creationdate": "2021-07-12T16:40:27-05:00", "id": 1500963, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2556253, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Blackspire", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-11-27T11:31:40-06:00", 2, "GazaC76"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 366, "id": 2587215, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "cogar328", "body": "I use the addon Dominos for my bar and had to disable it for Razorgore's interface to show up, never had to do that before, maybe a change with 8.0?", "date": "2018-08-02T12:30:35-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 367, "id": 2609470, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Tequima", "body": "As of 8.0 this encounter is once again broken unless you are VERY careful once you have finished clearing the eggs. I suggest you clear all the eggs: \r\n[ul]\r\n[li]On the platform with the control orb[/li]\r\n[li]In a line towards the far platform[/li]\r\n[li]On the far platform[/li]\r\n[li]Working in a zig-zag from the far platform back to the control orb[/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n\r\nMake sure you leave at least 10 seconds between releasing the mind control and killing Grethok the Controller or you will find him and you both dead and the gate still locked. You will have been saved to the instance [s]and will have to wait until reset to try again[/s]. Exit the the raid, wait for a soft reset (not sure how long as I went AFK to do some RL stuff for 15+ minutes). He should have respawned.\r\n\r\nAs other posters have noted, if you have a pet, dismiss it before you start this encounter.", "date": "2018-09-03T07:45:14-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The boss resets normally, so you don't need to leave the instance. Just wait a bit and it'll respawn.", "creationdate": "2018-11-26T11:25:59-06:00", "id": 1206551, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2609470, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "niqushortz", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 368, "id": 2855014, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "FaeTheWanderer", "body": "[b][u]Very Important Note For Any Class With a Pet:[/u][/b]\r\n\r\nYou must dismiss your pet before clicking the Orb of Domination to take control over Razorgore. If you have a pet out, the orb will appear clickable but will do nothing, allowing extra mobs to spawn in and start killing him before you get a chance to crack open those sweet, sweet eggs. The mobs die so easily at 120 that you can one-shot them with nearly any damaging ability anyway!\r\n\r\nAfter this fight feel free to summon in your best battle buddy to merrily trounce the rest of the raid!", "date": "2018-11-25T19:38:41-06:00", "rating": 60, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "That's why its never worked for me on my lock, was driving me nuts! thanks!", "creationdate": "2019-04-10T00:33:35-05:00", "id": 1228087, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2855014, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "luckypeters05", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "This worked PERFECTLY. Especially if you have a periodic shield from Azerite gear or simply don't take damage from the mobs.", "creationdate": "2020-01-10T12:15:52-06:00", "id": 1346838, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2855014, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Savistik", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "This needs many, many more upvotes or made a sticky at the top of the page.", "creationdate": "2020-05-30T23:02:31-05:00", "id": 1372145, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2855014, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Jeolene", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "This is the missing info I needed! Was able to solo it easy as a hunter once I dismissed my pet!", "creationdate": "2021-09-12T11:48:56-05:00", "id": 1511903, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2855014, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Linmoriel", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
