{"commentv2": 1, "number": 370, "id": 3172738, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "TheDonZone", "body": "Just an FYI...if you don't know this fight and you go in and 1-shot Razorgore, you will get 1-shot as well, and be unable to re-enter the encounter for about 10 minutes.  If you leave the dungeon, you will get an encounter in progress error when you try to go back in.  Once the 10 minutes has passed, you'll be able to get back in.", "date": "2019-11-20T20:49:03-06:00", "rating": 21, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I just had that brain fart...Thanks for the info", "creationdate": "2020-02-06T17:34:21-06:00", "id": 1353103, "rating": 2, "commentid": 3172738, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Blacknny", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I did this and went and cleared Molten Core and I still cannot zone in. Razorgore is considered defeated on the lockout.", "creationdate": "2020-11-15T02:25:01-06:00", "id": 1406255, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3172738, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "xLunacyx", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Dunno if anything changed but I just did this and so I just zoned out and reset all instances and it's back up", "creationdate": "2021-01-18T08:08:13-06:00", "id": 1442828, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3172738, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "sf1034", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
