{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 185644, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "MrAnime86", "body": "Now sells the recipes for Crunchy Serpent (http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31674) and Mok'Nathal Shortribs (http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31675) to both factions. \r\nThey are limited in supply however, so you may have to come back for them several times.", "date": "2007-11-16T08:15:49-06:00", "rating": 15, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "strange, i don't see the recipes there.  where else is horde suppose to go? :/", "creationdate": "2008-04-01T21:30:03-05:00", "id": 330770, "rating": 0, "commentid": 185644, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "138713", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "If you are Horde, you can easily do [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10860]Mok'Nathal Treats[/url], which will reward you with these recipes.  Regardless, the recipes sold are BoP so you won't find AH resellers camping the vendor.", "creationdate": "2008-04-10T08:04:11-05:00", "id": 30671, "rating": 9, "commentid": 185644, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "bookworm13", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just make sure you remember that these recipes are BoP...  I was tired when I got there, and was just excited that she had both recipes the first time I checked. I didn't realize until after I bought them that I couldn't send them to my one character with any cooking skill!", "creationdate": "2008-09-19T10:00:37-05:00", "id": 350539, "rating": 3, "commentid": 185644, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Wendy", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 673970, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Whittall", "body": "There is now an Unlimited stock of these things. Just found out passing by :).", "date": "2009-04-12T11:59:23-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Not true.  These are limited stock (3.1).", "creationdate": "2009-04-18T08:53:12-05:00", "id": 92102, "rating": 9, "commentid": 673970, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Aurlon", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 836147, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Anyu", "body": "Note that both Crunchy Serpent and Mok'Nathal Shortribs are BOP (will get soulbound after picking them up), so you won't be able to buy, then give them to your other characters.\r\nI hope this will save you some gold. (^_^)", "date": "2009-09-09T10:11:32-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": ".... and I just came here to mention this very thing. Fortunately, I only bought two sets. Unfortunately, the toon that bought them already knew them, tho I'm not sure how as she's never been here before...", "creationdate": "2012-07-20T19:15:53-05:00", "id": 558292, "rating": 0, "commentid": 836147, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Barleduq", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Wrong info on the products. You CAN purchase both on the AH. And then continue with cooking them quest for Rokk. (Dated 10-26-2020.)", "creationdate": "2020-10-26T12:54:37-05:00", "id": 1400365, "rating": 0, "commentid": 836147, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Tyrennis", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 983291, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "325838", "body": "You must make two recipes in order to complete Super Hot Stew for The Rokk in Shattrath. Buy some Serpent Flesh and Raptor ribs in the AH before going to Blade's Edge Mountains.\r\n\r\nFly to Everlook in Blade's Edge mountain. Vendor for the first 2 recipes, [b]Mok'Nathal Shortribs [/b]and [b]Crunchy Serpent [/b]are sold by [b]Xerintha Ravenoak[/b], directly west of the flight path at [b]62, 40[/b]. Cook them up.\r\n\r\nFly to Sylvanaar then head to Forge Camp Terror in the bottom left corner of Blade's Edge. Kill an [b]Abyssal Flamebringer[/b] (just find one on the edge to avoid flak fire). Click the cooking pot in your bag to cook it up. Quest is complete. Turn back into The Rock at 61, 16 in Lower City, Shattrath.", "date": "2010-02-23T01:54:55-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It's worth pointing out that you will be \"Ever looking\" if you're trying to find Everlook in Blade's Edge Mountains. That is in Winterspring.The camp you're looking for is \"Evergrove\". Also, should you have gotten here before picking up the mats from the AH, there are winged serpents and raptors directly south of your location - that will drop the required mats.", "creationdate": "2012-05-21T19:21:41-05:00", "id": 545088, "rating": 6, "commentid": 983291, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "digitalutopia1", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "@digitalutopia1 Very Punny", "creationdate": "2012-05-22T21:54:10-05:00", "id": 545329, "rating": 0, "commentid": 983291, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "tauna", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "And, while the raptors are numerous and have lots of ribs, the serpents are far fewer, and apparently have very little flesh on their bones. Lots of feathers tho, which is odd for scaled flying serpents.....", "creationdate": "2012-07-20T19:16:59-05:00", "id": 558293, "rating": 1, "commentid": 983291, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Barleduq", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-02-23T02:15:04-06:00", 2, "325838"]}
